JSCBDISP EQU 188                                                        00022000
JSCBAOS1 EQU  72                                                        00023000
JSCBAOS2 EQU 192                                                        00024000
*   PARMPTR=R1;                     /* SAVE ADDR OF PARM             */ 00025000
         LR    PARMPTR,R1                                          0064 00026000
*   GEN(MODESET MODE=SUP);          /* PUT INIT IN SUPV STATE        */ 00027000
*                                                                  0065 00028000
         MODESET MODE=SUP                                               00029000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00030000
*   /*                                                               */ 00031000
*   /* THE FOLLOWING SECTION OF CODE GETS CORE FOR AND INITIALIZES   */ 00032000
*   /* THE INITIATOR'S ENTRANCE,OPTIONS, AND EXIT LISTS.             */ 00033000
*   /*                                                               */ 00034000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00035000
*                                                                  0066 00036000
*   R0=LENGTH(IELLIST)+LENGTH(IELOPTS)+LENGTH(IELEXITS);/* LENGTH OF    00037000
*                                      THE IEL,IOL,AND IXL           */ 00038000
         LA    R0,48                                               0066 00039000
*   R0=R0|SUBPOOOL;                 /* OR IN SUBPOOL 255             */ 00040000
         O     R0,SUBPOOOL                                         0067 00041000
*   GEN(GETMAIN R,LV=(0));          /* GET CORE FOR THE IEL,IOL, AND    00042000
*                                      IXL                           */ 00043000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00044000
*   IELPTR=COREPTR;                 /* PUT CORE ADDR IN BASE REG     */ 00045000
         LR    IELPTR,COREPTR                                      0069 00046000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0070 00047000
*    (R0,                                                          0070 00048000
*     R1) UNRSTD;                                                  0070 00049000
*   IELLIST=''B;                    /* INITIALIZE ENTRANCE LIST TO 0 */ 00050000
         XC    IELLIST(24,IELPTR),IELLIST(IELPTR)                  0071 00051000
*   IELOPLST=ADDR(IELLIST)+LENGTH(IELLIST);/* SAVE THE ADDRESS OF THE   00052000
*                                      OPTIONS LIST IN THE IEL       */ 00053000
         LA    @15,24                                              0072 00054000
         ALR   @15,IELPTR                                          0072 00055000
         ST    @15,IELOPLST(,IELPTR)                               0072 00056000
*   IELEXIT=ADDR(IELOPTS)+LENGTH(IELOPTS);/* SAVE THE ADDRESS OF THE    00057000
*                                      EXIT LIST IN THE IEL          */ 00058000
         LA    @10,8                                               0073 00059000
         LR    @05,@15                                             0073 00060000
         ALR   @05,@10                                             0073 00061000
         ST    @05,IELEXIT(,IELPTR)                                0073 00062000
*   IELEND='1'B;                    /* SET END OF ENTRANCE LIST    0074 00063000
*                                      INDICATOR                     */ 00064000
         OI    IELEND(IELPTR),B'10000000'                          0074 00065000
*   IELOPTS=''B;                    /* INITIALIZE OPTIONS LIST TO 0  */ 00066000
         XC    IELOPTS(8,@15),IELOPTS(@15)                         0075 00067000
*   IELEXITS=''B;                   /* INITIALIZE EXIT LIST TO 0     */ 00068000
         L     @05,IELEXIT(,IELPTR)                                0076 00069000
         XC    IELEXITS(16,@05),IELEXITS(@05)                      0076 00070000
*   IELOPLEN=LENGTH(IELOPTS);       /* SAVE LENGTH OF OPTIONS LIST   */ 00071000
         STH   @10,IELOPLEN(,@15)                                  0077 00072000
*   IELXTLEN=LENGTH(IELEXITS);      /* SAVE LENGTH OF EXIT LIST      */ 00073000
         MVC   IELXTLEN(2,@05),@CH00042                            0078 00074000
*   IELRTNA=RTNREG;                 /* SAVE INITIATOR'S RETURN     0079 00075000
*                                      ADDRESS                       */ 00076000
         ST    RTNREG,IELRTNA(,IELPTR)                             0079 00077000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0080 00078000
*     RTNREG UNRSTD;                                               0080 00079000
*   IELSWAS=237;                    /* SWA SUBPOOL # TO BE USED FOR     00080000
*                                      ALL TASKS INITIATED BY THIS 0081 00081000
*                                      INITIATOR                     */ 00082000
         MVI   IELSWAS(@15),X'ED'                                  0081 00083000
*/* THIS SECTION OF CODE GETS CORE FOR THE SSOB HEADER AND SSIB AND     00084000
*   INITIALIZES THE SSIB WITH THE NAME OF THE SUBSYSTEM THAT IS    0082 00085000
*   TO SELECT JOBS FOR THIS INITIATOR.                               */ 00086000
*                                                                  0082 00087000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0082 00088000
*    (R0,                                                          0082 00089000
*     COREPTR) RSTD;                                               0082 00090000
*   R0=LENGTH(SSOB);                /* LENGTH OF SSOB HEADER         */ 00091000
         LA    R0,20                                               0083 00092000
*   R0=R0|SUBPOOOL;                 /* OR IN SUBPOOL 255             */ 00093000
         O     R0,SUBPOOOL                                         0084 00094000
*   GEN(GETMAIN R,LV=(0));          /* GET CORE FOR SSOB HEADER      */ 00095000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00096000
*   IELSSOBA=COREPTR;               /* PUT THE ADDRESS OF THE SSOB 0086 00097000
*                                      HEADER IN THE IEL             */ 00098000
         ST    COREPTR,IELSSOBA(,IELPTR)                           0086 00099000
*   SSOB=''B;                       /* ZERO SSOB HEADER              */ 00100000
         L     @10,IELSSOBA(,IELPTR)                               0087 00101000
         XC    SSOB(20,@10),SSOB(@10)                              0087 00102000
*   SSOBID=SSOBIDD;                 /* PUT THE SSOB ID IN THE SSOB   */ 00103000
         MVC   SSOBID(4,@10),@CC00050                              0088 00104000
*   SSOBLEN=LENGTH(SSOB);           /* SAVE LENGTH OF THE SSOB       */ 00105000
         MVC   SSOBLEN(2,@10),@CH01645                             0089 00106000
*   R0=LENGTH(SSIB);                /* LENGTH OF SSIB                */ 00107000
         LA    R0,36                                               0090 00108000
*   R0=R0|SUBPOOOL;                 /* OR IN SUBPOOL 255             */ 00109000
         O     R0,SUBPOOOL                                         0091 00110000
*   GEN(GETMAIN R,LV=(0));          /* GET CORE FOR SSIB             */ 00111000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00112000
*   SSOBSSIB=COREPTR;               /* PUT SSIB ADDR IN SSOB         */ 00113000
         L     @10,IELSSOBA(,IELPTR)                               0093 00114000
         ST    COREPTR,SSOBSSIB(,@10)                              0093 00115000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0094 00116000
*    (R0,                                                          0094 00117000
*     COREPTR) UNRSTD;                                             0094 00118000
*   SSIB=''B;                       /* INITIALIZE SSIB TO 0          */ 00119000
         L     @10,IELSSOBA(,IELPTR)                               0095 00120000

./  ADD  SSI=31431605,NAME=IEFIMASK
         TITLE 'IEFIMASK, CONVERT BIT MASK                           '  00001000
IEFIMASK CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IEFIMASK  73.143'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00013000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00014000
         LR    @11,@01                                             0001 00015000
         USING @DATD,@11                                           0001 00016000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00017000
         MVC   @PC00001(16),0(@01)                                 0001 00018000
*   BITSLOCL=BITS;                  /* COPY SO THE ORIGINAL VERSION     00019000
*                                      WILL BE PRESERVED             */ 00020000
         L     @10,@PC00001                                        0011 00021000
         MVC   BITSLOCL(2),BITS(@10)                               0011 00022000
*   LISTPOS=0;                                                     0012 00023000
         SR    LISTPOS,LISTPOS                                     0012 00024000
*   DO BITPOS=1 TO NUMBITS;         /* BITPOS REPRESENTS THE ORIGINAL   00025000
*                                      POSITION OF THE BIT NOW AT  0013 00026000
*                                      BITONE                        */ 00027000
         LA    BITPOS,1                                            0013 00028000
         B     @DE00013                                            0013 00029000
@DL00013 DS    0H                                                  0014 00030000
*     IF BITONE='1'B THEN                                          0014 00031000
         TM    BITONE,B'10000000'                                  0014 00032000
         BNO   @RF00014                                            0014 00033000
*       DO;                         /* IF BIT IS ON SET ITS INDEX IN    00034000
*                                      THE LIST                      */ 00035000
*                                                                  0015 00036000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00037000
*         /*                                                         */ 00038000
*         /* SOME SPECIAL PROCESSING IS REQUIRED TO ACCOUNT FOR THE  */ 00039000
*         /* FACT THAT THE NUMBER OF COMMAS IS ONE LESS THAN THE     */ 00040000
*         /* NUMBER OF ELEMENTS IN THE LIST. THIS MODULE HAS SPECIAL */ 00041000
*         /* PROCESSING FOR THE SETTING OF THE FIRST ELEMENT OF THE  */ 00042000
*         /* LIST. OTHER SOLUTIONS WERE REJECTED FOR ONE OF THE      */ 00043000
*         /* FOLLOWING REASONS: (1) ONE OR MORE EXTRA COMMAS WOULD BE*/ 00044000
*         /* SET AFTER THE LAST ELEMENT IF NOT ALL THE BITS ARE ON.  */ 00045000
*         /* (2) AN EXTRA LOOP WOULD BE REQUIRED TO COUNT THE NUMBER */ 00046000
*         /* OF COMMAS REQUIRED OR TO SET THE COMMAS SEPARATELY.     */ 00047000
*         /*                                                         */ 00048000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00049000
*                                                                  0016 00050000
*         IF LISTPOS=0 THEN                                        0016 00051000
         LTR   LISTPOS,LISTPOS                                     0016 00052000
         BNZ   @RF00016                                            0016 00053000
*           CPUZERO=CONVCHAR(BITPOS);/* SET FIRST ELEMENT IN LIST    */ 00054000
         L     @10,@PC00001+8                                      0017 00055000
         LA    @01,CONVCHAR-1(BITPOS)                              0017 00056000
         MVC   CPUZERO(1,@10),0(@01)                               0017 00057000
*         ELSE                                                     0018 00058000
*           DO;                     /* SET ELEMENT WHICH IS NOT FIRST   00059000
*                                      ELEMENT IN LIST (PRECEEDED BY    00060000
*                                      A COMMA)                      */ 00061000
         B     @RC00016                                            0018 00062000
@RF00016 DS    0H                                                  0019 00063000
*             COMMA(LISTPOS)=COMMAC;                               0019 00064000
         LR    @10,LISTPOS                                         0019 00065000
         AR    @10,@10                                             0019 00066000
         L     @15,@PC00001+8                                      0019 00067000
         ST    @10,@TF00001                                        0019 00068000
         ALR   @10,@15                                             0019 00069000
         AL    @10,@CF00063                                        0019 00070000
         MVI   COMMA-1(@10),C','                                   0019 00071000
*             ELEMENT(LISTPOS)=CONVCHAR(BITPOS);                   0020 00072000
         AL    @15,@TF00001                                        0020 00073000
         LA    @10,CONVCHAR-1(BITPOS)                              0020 00074000
         MVC   ELEMENT-2(1,@15),0(@10)                             0020 00075000
*           END;                                                   0021 00076000
*         LISTPOS=LISTPOS+1;        /* INCREMENT INDEX IN OUTPUT   0022 00077000
*                                      LIST, AFTER SETTING AN ELEMENT*/ 00078000
@RC00016 AH    LISTPOS,@CH00043                                    0022 00079000
*       END;                                                       0023 00080000
*     BITSLOCL=2*BITSLOCL;          /* SHIFT LEFT ONE POSITION, SO WE   00081000
*                                      CAN CHECK THE HIGH ORDER BIT  */ 00082000
@RF00014 SR    @10,@10                                             0024 00083000
         ICM   @10,3,BITSLOCL                                      0024 00084000
         AR    @10,@10                                             0024 00085000
         STH   @10,BITSLOCL                                        0024 00086000
*   END;                                                           0025 00087000
         AH    BITPOS,@CH00043                                     0025 00088000
@DE00013 L     @10,@PC00001+4                                      0025 00089000
         CH    BITPOS,NUMBITS(,@10)                                0025 00090000
         BNH   @DL00013                                            0025 00091000
*   NUMLIST=LISTPOS;                /* RETURN NUMBER OF ELEMENTS PUT    00092000
*                                      IN LIST. (THIS IS ONE GREATER    00093000
*                                      THAN THE LAST INDEX USED    0026 00094000
*                                      BECAUSE THE COUNT MUST START     00095000
*                                      AT 1 INSTEAD OF 0.)           */ 00096000
         L     @10,@PC00001+12                                     0026 00097000
         STH   LISTPOS,NUMLIST(,@10)                               0026 00098000
*   END;                                                           0027 00099000
@EL00001 DS    0H                                                  0027 00100000
@EF00001 L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0027 00101000
         LR    @01,@11                                             0027 00102000
         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00103000
@ER00001 LM    @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0027 00104000
         BR    @14                                                 0027 00105000
@DATA    DS    0H                                                       00106000
@CH00043 DC    H'1'                                                     00107000
@DATD    DSECT                                                          00108000
         DS    0F                                                       00109000
@PC00001 DS    4F                                                       00110000
@TF00001 DS    F                                                        00111000
IEFIMASK CSECT                                                          00112000
         DS    0F                                                       00113000
@CF00063 DC    F'-1'                                                    00114000
@DATD    DSECT                                                          00115000
         DS    0D                                                       00116000
BITSLOCL DS    CL2                                                      00117000
         ORG   BITSLOCL                                                 00118000
BITONE   DS    BL1                                                      00119000
@NM00002 EQU   BITSLOCL+0                                               00120000
         ORG   BITSLOCL+2                                               00121000
IEFIMASK CSECT                                                          00122000
         DS    0F                                                       00123000
@SIZDATD DC    AL1(0)                                                   00124000
         DC    AL3(@ENDDATD-@DATD)                                      00125000
         DS    0D                                                       00126000
CONVCHAR DC    CL16'0123456789ABCDEF'                                   00127000
IEFIMASK CSECT                                                          00128000
         DS   0H                                                        00129000
PATCHLOC DC (25)X'00'                                                   00130000
@DATD    DSECT                                                          00131000
         ORG   *+1-(*-@DATD)/(*-@DATD) INSURE DSECT DATA                00132000
@ENDDATD EQU   *                                                        00133000
IEFIMASK CSECT                                                          00134000
@00      EQU   00                      EQUATES FOR REGISTERS 0-15       00135000
@01      EQU   01                                                       00136000
@02      EQU   02                                                       00137000
@03      EQU   03                                                       00138000
@04      EQU   04                                                       00139000
@05      EQU   05                                                       00140000
@06      EQU   06                                                       00141000
@07      EQU   07                                                       00142000
@08      EQU   08                                                       00143000
@09      EQU   09                                                       00144000
@10      EQU   10                                                       00145000
@11      EQU   11                                                       00146000
@12      EQU   12                                                       00147000
@13      EQU   13                                                       00148000
@14      EQU   14                                                       00149000
@15      EQU   15                                                       00150000
LISTPOS  EQU   @02                                                      00151000
BITPOS   EQU   @03                                                      00152000
BITS     EQU   0                                                        00153000
NUMBITS  EQU   0                                                        00154000
LIST     EQU   0                                                        00155000
CPUZERO  EQU   LIST                                                     00156000
@NM00001 EQU   LIST+1                                                   00157000
COMMA    EQU   @NM00001                                                 00158000
ELEMENT  EQU   @NM00001+1                                               00159000
NUMLIST  EQU   0                                                        00160000
@ENDDATA EQU   *                                                        00161000
         END   IEFIMASK                                                 00162000
./  ADD  SSI=63350793,NAME=IEFIRECM
         TITLE 'IEFIRECM - INITIATOR RESOURCE MANAGER                  *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IEFIRECM CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(24)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IEFIRECM 76335  UZ06235 '                         0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00014000
         GETMAIN  R,LV=(0)                                              00015000
         LR    @11,@01                                             0001 00016000
         USING @DATD,@11                                           0001 00017000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00018000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00019000
         ST    @11,8(,@13)                                         0001 00020000
         LR    @13,@11                                             0001 00021000
         MVC   @PC00001(4),0(@01)                                  0001 00022000
*   RESTAE(1:SESTAE)=LESTAE(1:SESTAE);/* MOVE IN ESTAE LIST          */ 00023000
         L     @14,SESTAE                                          0024 00024000
         BCTR  @14,0                                               0024 00025000
         EX    @14,@SM01272                                        0024 00026000
*   R6=ADDR(IEFISEXR);              /* POINT R6 TO EXIT ROUTINE      */ 00027000
         L     R6,@CV01157                                         0025 00028000
*   R4=0;                           /* ZERO PARAMETER LIST INDICATES    00029000
*                                      INITATOR RESOURE MANAGER IN 0026 00030000
*                                      CONTROL                       */ 00031000
         SLR   R4,R4                                               0026 00032000
*   R1=ADDR(RESTAE);                /* POINT TO ESTAE PARAMETER LIST */ 00033000
         LA    R1,RESTAE                                           0027 00034000
*   GEN( ESTAE (6),PARAM=(4),XCTL=YES,RECORD=YES,MF=(E,(1)));      0028 00035000
          ESTAE (6),PARAM=(4),XCTL=YES,RECORD=YES,MF=(E,(1))            00036000
*   IF R15¬=0 THEN                  /* IF ESTAE FAILS RETURN TO    0029 00037000
*                                      CALLER                        */ 00038000
         LTR   R15,R15                                             0029 00039000
         BZ    @RF00029                                            0029 00040000
*     RETURN CODE(4);               /* RETURN TO RTM                 */ 00041000
         L     @13,4(,@13)                                         0030 00042000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0030 00043000
         LR    @01,@11                                             0030 00044000
         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00045000
         LA    @15,4                                               0030 00046000
         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0030 00047000
         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0030 00048000
         BR    @14                                                 0030 00049000
*   ENQCORE(1:ENQLGTH)=ENQLIST(1:ENQLGTH);/* MOVE IN ENQ LIST        */ 00050000
@RF00029 L     @14,ENQLGTH                                         0031 00051000
         BCTR  @14,0                                               0031 00052000
         EX    @14,@SM01274                                        0031 00053000
*   R1=ADDR(ENQCORE);               /* POINT TO ENQ PARAMETER LIST   */ 00054000
         LA    R1,ENQCORE                                          0032 00055000
*   GEN( ENQ MF=(E,(1)));           /* ISSUE ENQ ON CSCB CHAIN       */ 00056000
          ENQ MF=(E,(1))                                                00057000
*   RFY                                                            0034 00058000
*    (R1,                                                          0034 00059000
*     R4,                                                          0034 00060000
*     R6,                                                          0034 00061000
*     R15) UNRSTD;                                                 0034 00062000
*   CSCBPTR=BACHN;                  /* POINT TO FIRST CSCB ON CHAIN  */ 00063000
         L     @10,CVTPTR                                          0035 00064000
         L     @10,CVTMSER(,@10)                                   0035 00065000
         L     CSCBPTR,BACHN(,@10)                                 0035 00066000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0036 00067000
*     ASCB BASED(RMPLASCB);         /* BASE THE ASCB                 */ 00068000
*   ASCBCSCB=0;                     /* CLEAR THE CSCB POINTER IN ASCB*/ 00069000
         SLR   @10,@10                                             0037 00070000
         L     @09,@PC00001                                        0037 00071000
         L     @09,RMPLASCB(,@09)                                  0037 00072000
         ST    @10,ASCBCSCB(,@09)                                  0037 00073000
*   ASCBJBNI=0;                     /* CLEAR THE GTF FIELDS IN ASCB  */ 00074000
         ST    @10,ASCBJBNI(,@09)                                  0038 00075000
*   ASCBJBNS=0;                     /* INDICATE THE JOB IS DONE TO 0039 00076000
*                                      GTF                           */ 00077000
         ST    @10,ASCBJBNS(,@09)                                  0039 00078000
*   DO WHILE CSCBPTR¬=0;            /* LOOP DOWN THE CSCB CHAIN      */ 00079000
         B     @DE00040                                            0040 00080000
@DL00040 DS    0H                                                  0041 00081000
*     IF CHASID=RMPLASID THEN                                      0041 00082000
         L     @10,@PC00001                                        0041 00083000
         LH    @10,RMPLASID(,@10)                                  0041 00084000
         N     @10,@CF01276                                        0041 00085000
         CH    @10,CHASID(,CSCBPTR)                                0041 00086000
         BNE   @RF00041                                            0041 00087000
*       DO;                         /* IF THIS CSCB IS IN THIS MEMORY   00088000
*                                      THEN DELETE IT FROM SYSTEM    */ 00089000
*         CHDL='1'B;                /* INDICATE DELETE THIS CSCB     */ 00090000
*         CHFC='1'B;                /* INDICATE FREE THIS CSCBS AREA */ 00091000
         OI    CHDL(CSCBPTR),B'00000110'                           0044 00092000
*                                                                  0045 00093000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00094000
*         /*                                                         */ 00095000
*         /* WTO THE MSG                                     @YM07219*/ 00096000
*         /*                                                         */ 00097000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00098000
*                                                                  0045 00099000
*         MESSPTR=ADDR(MESCORE);    /* POINT TO AREA TO BUILD MESSAGE*/ 00100000
         LA    MESSPTR,MESCORE                                     0045 00101000
*         MESAREA=MESAREA&&MESAREA; /* CLEAR THE WTO AREA            */ 00102000
         XC    MESAREA(76,MESSPTR),MESAREA(MESSPTR)                0046 00103000
*         MESLEN=LENGTH(MESAREA)-4; /* PUT LENGTH OF WTO IN AREA     */ 00104000
         MVC   MESLEN(2,MESSPTR),@CH01226                          0047 00105000
*         MESFLGS=MCSFLGS;          /* MOVE IN THE MCS FLAGS         */ 00106000
         LA    @10,LABEL1                                          0048 00107000
         MVC   MESFLGS(2,MESSPTR),MCSFLGS(@10)                     0048 00108000
*         PROCNAME=CHCLS;           /* MOVE IN THE PROC OR JOB NAME  */ 00109000
         MVC   PROCNAME(8,MESSPTR),CHCLS(CSCBPTR)                  0049 00110000
*         IF CHCLS=CHKEY THEN       /* IF THEY ARE EQUAL THEN REGULAR   00111000
*                                      JOB                           */ 00112000
         CLC   CHCLS(8,CSCBPTR),CHKEY(CSCBPTR)                     0050 00113000
         BNE   @RF00050                                            0050 00114000
*           DO;                                                    0051 00115000
*             BASEPTR=ADDR(DOT);    /* POINT TO AREA TO BUILD NEXT 0052 00116000
*                                      SECTION                       */ 00117000
         LA    BASEPTR,DOT(,MESSPTR)                               0052 00118000
*             IF CHCLS=ZEROS THEN                                  0053 00119000
         CLC   CHCLS(8,CSCBPTR),ZEROS                              0053 00120000
         BNE   @RF00053                                            0053 00121000
*               DO;                 /* IF NO NAME IN CSCB            */ 00122000
*                 COMMAND=COMMANDN; /* MOVE IN COMMAND NAME          */ 00123000
         MVC   COMMAND(10),COMMANDN                                0055 00124000
*                 IF CHVCD=START THEN/* IF START COMMAND PUT START IN   00125000
*                                      MSG                           */ 00126000
         CLC   CHVCD(1,CSCBPTR),START                              0056 00127000
         BNE   @RF00056                                            0056 00128000
*                   VERB=STARTN;    /* MOVE START TO MSG             */ 00129000
         MVC   VERB(7),STARTN                                      0057 00130000
*                 ELSE                                             0058 00131000
*                   IF CHVCD=MOUNT THEN/* MOVE MOUNT NAME IN         */ 00132000
         B     @RC00056                                            0058 00133000
@RF00056 CLC   CHVCD(1,CSCBPTR),MOUNT                              0058 00134000
         BNE   @RF00058                                            0058 00135000
*                     VERB=MOUNTN;  /* MOVE IN MOUNT NAME            */ 00136000
         MVC   VERB(7),MOUNTN                                      0059 00137000
*                   ELSE                                           0060 00138000
*                     IF CHVCD=LOGON THEN/* MOVE IN LOGON            */ 00139000
         B     @RC00058                                            0060 00140000
@RF00058 CLC   CHVCD(1,CSCBPTR),LOGON                              0060 00141000
         BNE   @RF00060                                            0060 00142000
*                       VERB=LOGONN;/* SHOULD BE A LOGON             */ 00143000
         MVC   VERB(7),LOGONN                                      0061 00144000
*                 HEADAREA=ADDRESS; /* MOVE IN NAME ADDRESS SPACE    */ 00145000
@RF00060 DS    0H                                                  0062 00146000
@RC00058 DS    0H                                                  0062 00147000
@RC00056 MVC   HEADAREA(17,MESSPTR),ADDRESS                        0062 00148000
*                 BASEPTR=ADDR(BUILDA);/* UPDATE BASEPTR             */ 00149000
         LA    BASEPTR,BUILDA(,MESSPTR)                            0063 00150000
*               END;                                               0064 00151000
*             ELSE                                                 0065 00152000
*               MESLEN=MESLEN-9;    /* SUBTRACT NINE FROM THE MESSAGE   00153000
*                                      LENGTH                        */ 00154000
         B     @RC00053                                            0065 00155000
@RF00053 LH    @10,MESLEN(,MESSPTR)                                0065 00156000
         SL    @10,@CF00951                                        0065 00157000
         STH   @10,MESLEN(,MESSPTR)                                0065 00158000
*           END;                                                   0066 00159000
*         ELSE                                                     0067 00160000
*           DO;                     /* STARTED TASK, PROC.TASKNAME IN   00161000
*                                      MSG                           */ 00162000
         B     @RC00050                                            0067 00163000
@RF00050 DS    0H                                                  0068 00164000
*             DOT=DOTT;             /* MOVE IN THE PERIOD            */ 00165000
         MVC   DOT(1,MESSPTR),DOTT                                 0068 00166000
*             TASKNAME=CHKEY;       /* MOVE IN THE JOBNAME           */ 00167000
         MVC   TASKNAME(8,MESSPTR),CHKEY(CSCBPTR)                  0069 00168000
*             BASEPTR=ADDR(BUILDA); /* AREA TO BUILD NEXT SECTION OF    00169000
*                                      MSG                           */ 00170000
         LA    BASEPTR,BUILDA(,MESSPTR)                            0070 00171000
*           END;                                                   0071 00172000
*         RFY                                                      0072 00173000
*           R1 RSTD;                /*                       @G17FPSS*/ 00174000
@RC00050 DS    0H                                                  0073 00175000
*         R1=ADDR(ENQCORE);         /* POINT TO DEQ PARAMETER LIST   */ 00176000
         LA    R1,ENQCORE                                          0073 00177000
*         GEN(DEQ MF=(E,(1)));      /* ISSUE DEQ OFF CSCB CHAIN      */ 00178000
         DEQ MF=(E,(1))                                                 00179000
*         RFY                                                      0075 00180000
*           R1 UNRSTD;              /*                       @G17FPSS*/ 00181000
*                                                                  0076 00182000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00183000
*         /*                                                         */ 00184000
*         /* CONVERT THE ASID TO PRINTABLE CHARACTERS                */ 00185000
*         /*                                                         */ 00186000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00187000
*                                                                  0076 00188000
*         RFY                                                      0076 00189000
*           R7 RSTD;                /*                       @G17FPSS*/ 00190000
*         R7=RMPLASID;              /* PICK UP THE ASID      @G17FPSS*/ 00191000
         L     @10,@PC00001                                        0077 00192000
         LH    R7,RMPLASID(,@10)                                   0077 00193000
         N     R7,@CF01276                                         0077 00194000
*         CVD(R7,UNPACK);           /* CONVERT ASID TO DECIMAL     0078 00195000
*                                                            @G17FPSS*/ 00196000
         CVD   R7,UNPACK                                           0078 00197000
*         UNPK(ASIDAREA,UNPACK(5:8));/* UNPACK THE ASID      @G17FPSS*/ 00198000
         UNPK  ASIDAREA(4),UNPACK+4(4)                             0079 00199000
*         GEN REFS(ASIDAREA)(OI ASIDAREA+3,X'F0');/* MAKE LAST DIGIT    00200000
*                                      A VALID NUMBER        @G17FPSS*/ 00201000
         OI ASIDAREA+3,X'F0'                                            00202000
*         RFY                                                      0081 00203000
*           R7 UNRSTD;              /*                       @G17FPSS*/ 00204000
*         DESCFGS=DESCDS;           /* MOVE IN THE DESCRIPTOR FLAGS     00205000
*                                                            @ZD00106*/ 00206000
         LA    @10,LABEL1                                          0082 00207000
         MVC   DESCFGS(2,BASEPTR),DESCDS(@10)                      0082 00208000
*         ROUTFLGS=ROUTCDS;         /* MOVE IN THE ROUT CODES      0083 00209000
*                                                            @ZD00106*/ 00210000
*                                                                  0083 00211000
         MVC   ROUTFLGS(2,BASEPTR),ROUTCDS(@10)                    0083 00212000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00213000
*         /*                                                         */ 00214000
*         /* DETERMINE WHICH TEXT OF MESSAGE TO USE                  */ 00215000
*         /*                                                         */ 00216000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00217000
*                                                                  0084 00218000
*         IF ASCBMCC(2:3)=FORCEA22 THEN/* WAS THIS ADDRESS SPACE   0084 00219000
*                                      FORCED?               @G17FPSS*/ 00220000
         L     @10,@PC00001                                        0084 00221000
         L     @10,RMPLASCB(,@10)                                  0084 00222000
         CLC   ASCBMCC+1(2,@10),FORCEA22                           0084 00223000
         BNE   @RF00084                                            0084 00224000
*           DO;                     /* YES                   @G17FPSS*/ 00225000
*             MESID=FORMSGID;       /* MOVE IN FORCE MSG ID  @G17FPSS*/ 00226000
         MVC   MESID(8,MESSPTR),FORMSGID                           0086 00227000
*             FAILSPOT=FORCEMSG;    /* MOVE IN FORCED MESSAGE      0087 00228000
*                                                            @ZA13430*/ 00229000
         MVC   FAILSPOT(16,BASEPTR),FORCEMSG                       0087 00230000
*             RFY                                                  0088 00231000
*               WTOMAP BASED(ADDR(LABEL2));/* MAP FORCE WTO LIST FORM   00232000
*                                                            @ZD00106*/ 00233000
*             MESFLGS=MCSFLGS;      /* MOVE IN FLAGS TO GO TO MASTER    00234000
*                                      CONSOLE.              @ZD00106*/ 00235000
         LA    @10,LABEL2                                          0089 00236000
         MVC   MESFLGS(2,MESSPTR),MCSFLGS(@10)                     0089 00237000
*             DESCFGS=DESCDS;       /* MOVE IN FORCE'S DESC CODES  0090 00238000
*                                                            @ZD00106*/ 00239000
         MVC   DESCFGS(2,BASEPTR),DESCDS(@10)                      0090 00240000
*           END;                                                   0091 00241000
*         ELSE                      /* ADDRESS SPACE TERMINATED    0092 00242000
*                                                            @G17FPSS*/ 00243000
*           DO;                                                    0092 00244000
         B     @RC00084                                            0092 00245000
@RF00084 DS    0H                                                  0093 00246000
*             MESID=MSGID;          /* MOVE IN THE MSG ID            */ 00247000
         MVC   MESID(8,MESSPTR),MSGID                              0093 00248000
*             FAILSPOT=FAILMSG;     /* MOVE IN 1ST HALF FAIL MSG   0094 00249000
*                                                            @ZA13430*/ 00250000
         MVC   FAILSPOT(16,BASEPTR),FAILMSG                        0094 00251000
*           END;                    /*                       @ZA13430*/ 00252000
*         UNPK(UNPACK(1:5),ASCBMCC(2:4));/* UNPACK MEMORY TERM ABEND    00253000
*                                      CODE, CODE IS X'00XXX000'   0096 00254000
*                                                            @ZA13430*/ 00255000
@RC00084 L     @10,@PC00001                                        0096 00256000
         L     @10,RMPLASCB(,@10)                                  0096 00257000
         UNPK  UNPACK(5),ASCBMCC+1(3,@10)                          0096 00258000
*         TR(UNPACK(1:3),TRTABLE);  /* TRANSLATE CODE TO PRINTABLE 0097 00259000
*                                      CHARACTERS            @ZA13430*/ 00260000
         LA    @10,TRPATN                                          0097 00261000
         AL    @10,@CF01277                                        0097 00262000
         TR    UNPACK(3),TRTABLE(@10)                              0097 00263000
*         FAILCODE=UNPACK(1:3);     /* MOVE ABEND CODE TO MSG OUTPUT    00264000
*                                      AREA                  @ZA13430*/ 00265000
         MVC   FAILCODE(3,BASEPTR),UNPACK                          0098 00266000
*         ASIDHEAD=ADDRMSG;         /* MOVE IN ADDR SPACE HEADER   0099 00267000
*                                      MESSAGE               @G17FPSS*/ 00268000
         MVC   ASIDHEAD(20,BASEPTR),ADDRMSG                        0099 00269000
*         TERMASID=ASIDAREA;        /* MOVE IN THE ASID NUMBER     0100 00270000
*                                                            @G17FPSS*/ 00271000
         MVC   TERMASID(4,BASEPTR),ASIDAREA                        0100 00272000
*                                                                  0101 00273000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00274000
*         /*                                                         */ 00275000
*         /* ISSUE THE MESSAGE                                       */ 00276000
*         /*                                                         */ 00277000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00278000
*                                                                  0101 00279000
*         RFY                                                      0101 00280000
*          (R0,                                                    0101 00281000
*           R1) RSTD;               /*                       @ZD00106*/ 00282000
*         R1=MESSPTR;               /* POINT TO THE MESSAGE          */ 00283000
         LR    R1,MESSPTR                                          0102 00284000
*         R0=0;                     /* PUT IN CONSOLE ID.(MASTER   0103 00285000
*                                      CONSOLE)              @ZD00106*/ 00286000
         SLR   R0,R0                                               0103 00287000
*         GEN REFS(R1)(WTO MF=(E,(1)));/* WRITE MESSAGE TO OPERATOR  */ 00288000
         WTO MF=(E,(1))                                                 00289000
*                                                                  0105 00290000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00291000
*         /*                                                         */ 00292000
*         /* NOW ISSUE THE MGCR TO DELETE THE CSCB                   */ 00293000
*         /*                                                         */ 00294000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00295000
*                                                                  0105 00296000
*         R1=CSCBPTR;               /* POINT TO THE CSCB TO DELETE   */ 00297000
         LR    R1,CSCBPTR                                          0105 00298000
*         GEN(MGCR (1),CHAIN);      /* ISSUE SVC 34                  */ 00299000
         MGCR (1),CHAIN                                                 00300000
*         R1=ADDR(ENQCORE);         /* NOW ENQ BACK ON THE CSCB CHAIN*/ 00301000
         LA    R1,ENQCORE                                          0107 00302000
*         GEN(ENQ MF=(E,(1)));      /* ISSUE THE ENQ TO FIND NEXT  0108 00303000
*                                      CSCB                          */ 00304000
         ENQ MF=(E,(1))                                                 00305000
*         CSCBPTR=BACHN;            /* POINT TO THE FIRST CSCB       */ 00306000
         L     @10,CVTPTR                                          0109 00307000
         L     @10,CVTMSER(,@10)                                   0109 00308000
         L     CSCBPTR,BACHN(,@10)                                 0109 00309000
*         RFY                                                      0110 00310000
*          (R0,                                                    0110 00311000
*           R1) UNRSTD;             /*                       @ZD00106*/ 00312000
*       END;                                                       0111 00313000
*     ELSE                                                         0112 00314000
*       CSCBPTR=CHPTR;              /* UPDATE CSCB POINTER TO NEXT 0112 00315000
*                                      CSCB, IF THIS CSCB IS NOT IN     00316000
*                                      THIS MEMORY                   */ 00317000
         B     @RC00041                                            0112 00318000
@RF00041 L     CSCBPTR,CHPTR(,CSCBPTR)                             0112 00319000
*   END;                                                           0113 00320000
*                                                                  0113 00321000
@RC00041 DS    0H                                                  0113 00322000
@DE00040 LTR   CSCBPTR,CSCBPTR                                     0113 00323000
         BNZ   @DL00040                                            0113 00324000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00325000
*   /*                                                               */ 00326000
*   /* WE HAVE LOOPED DOWN THE CSCB CHAIN TO THE END, NOW DEQ        */ 00327000
*   /*                                                               */ 00328000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00329000
*                                                                  0114 00330000
*   RFY                                                            0114 00331000
*     R1 RSTD;                      /*                       @G17FPSS*/ 00332000
*   R1=ADDR(ENQCORE);               /* POINT TO DEQ PARAMETER LIST   */ 00333000
         LA    R1,ENQCORE                                          0115 00334000
*   GEN(DEQ MF=(E,(1)));            /* ISSUE THE DEQ FROM THE CSCB 0116 00335000
*                                      CHAIN                         */ 00336000
         DEQ MF=(E,(1))                                                 00337000
*   RFY                                                            0117 00338000
*     R1 UNRSTD;                    /*                       @G17FPSS*/ 00339000
*                                                                  0117 00340000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00341000
*   /*                                                               */ 00342000
*   /* NOW DELETE THE ESTAE ENVIRONMENT                              */ 00343000
*   /*                                                               */ 00344000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00345000
*                                                                  0118 00346000
*   GEN( ESTAE 0);                  /* ISSUE ESTAE ZERO TO DELETE  0118 00347000
*                                      ESTAE                         */ 00348000
          ESTAE 0                                                       00349000
*   RETURN CODE(0);                 /* RETURN TO RTM                 */ 00350000
         L     @13,4(,@13)                                         0119 00351000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0119 00352000
         LR    @01,@11                                             0119 00353000
         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00354000
         SLR   @15,@15                                             0119 00355000
         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0119 00356000
         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0119 00357000
         BR    @14                                                 0119 00358000
*   END                                                            0120 00359000

./  ADD  SSI=30661737,NAME=IEFISEXR
         TITLE 'IEFISEXR - INITATOR SUBSYSTEM EXIT ROUTINE           '  00001000
IEFISEXR CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IEFISEXR  73.066'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00009000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00010000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00011000
*   SDWAPTR=R1;                     /* POINT TO SDWA                 */ 00012000
         LR    SDWAPTR,R1                                          0009 00013000
*   R7=R14;                         /* SAVE THE RETURN ADDRESS       */ 00014000
         LR    R7,R14                                              0010 00015000
*   IF(R0=12)THEN                   /* IF NO SDWA RETURN             */ 00016000
         CH    R0,@CH00431                                         0011 00017000
         BNE   @RF00011                                            0011 00018000
*     R15=0;                        /* INDICATE NO RETRY             */ 00019000
         SR    R15,R15                                             0012 00020000
*   ELSE                                                           0013 00021000
*     DO;                                                          0013 00022000
*                                                                  0013 00023000
         B     @RC00011                                            0013 00024000
@RF00011 DS    0H                                                  0014 00025000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00026000
*       /*                                                           */ 00027000
*       /* AUTOMATIC STORAGE MUST BE EXPLICITLY GOTTEN AND FREED     */ 00028000
*       /* BECAUSE BOTH REGISTERS 0 ND 1 UPON ENTRY TO THIS MODULE   */ 00029000
*       /* CONTAIN INPUT, AND THE PLS GETMAIN WOULD DESTROY THEN     */ 00030000
*       /*                                                           */ 00031000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00032000
*                                                                  0014 00033000
*       GEN;                                                       0014 00034000
     L    R0,@SIZDATD                                                   00035000
     GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                                   00036000
     LR   R11,R1                                                        00037000
     USING  @DATD,R11                                                   00038000
*                                                                  0015 00039000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00040000
*       /*                                                           */ 00041000
*       /* CHECK FOR PROGRAM CHECK OR RESTART                        */ 00042000
*       /*                                                           */ 00043000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00044000
*                                                                  0015 00045000
*       IF SDWAPCHK='1'B|SDWARKEY='1'B THEN                        0015 00046000
         TM    SDWAPCHK(SDWAPTR),B'01100000'                       0015 00047000
         BZ    @RF00015                                            0015 00048000
*         DO;                                                      0016 00049000
*           SSDUMPC(1:SLSDUMP)=SSDUMP(1:SLSDUMP);/* MOVE IN SDUMP  0017 00050000
*                                      PARMS                         */ 00051000
         L     @10,SLSDUMP                                         0017 00052000
         BCTR  @10,0                                               0017 00053000
         EX    @10,@SM00452                                        0017 00054000
*           R1=ADDR(SSDUMPC);       /* POINT TO SDUMP PARAMETER      */ 00055000
         LA    R1,SSDUMPC                                          0018 00056000
*           GEN(SDUMP MF=(E,(1)));  /* ISSUE THE SDUMP               */ 00057000
         SDUMP MF=(E,(1))                                               00058000
*         END;                                                     0020 00059000
*                                                                  0020 00060000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00061000
*       /*                                                           */ 00062000
*       /* DEQ OFF CSCB , IT MAY BE HELD                             */ 00063000
*       /*                                                           */ 00064000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00065000
*                                                                  0021 00066000
*       DEQCORE(1:DEQLGTH)=DEQLIST(1:DEQLGTH);/* MOVE IN DEQ         */ 00067000
@RF00015 L     @10,DEQLGTH                                         0021 00068000
         BCTR  @10,0                                               0021 00069000
         EX    @10,@SM00454                                        0021 00070000
*       R1=ADDR(DEQCORE);           /* POINT TO DEQ PARAMETER LIST   */ 00071000
         LA    R1,DEQCORE                                          0022 00072000
*       GEN(DEQ MF=(E,(1)));        /* ISSUE THE DEQ                 */ 00073000
         DEQ MF=(E,(1))                                                 00074000
*                                                                  0024 00075000
*/*   ISSUE SETRP TO RECORD ERROR ON LOGREC                          */ 00076000
*                                                                  0024 00077000
*       IF SDWAPARM=0 THEN          /* IF PARMETER IS ZERO THE THIS     00078000
*                                      IS THE INITATOR RESOURE     0024 00079000
*                                      MANAGER                       */ 00080000
         SR    @10,@10                                             0024 00081000
         C     @10,SDWAPARM(,SDWAPTR)                              0024 00082000
         BNE   @RF00024                                            0024 00083000
*         DO;                       /* SETRP RECPARM(IRECM)        0025 00084000
*                                      RECORD(YES) RC(0)           0025 00085000
*                                      WKAREA(SDWAPTR)               */ 00086000
*           RESPECIFY                                              0026 00087000
*            (GPR00P,                                              0026 00088000
*             GPR01P,                                              0026 00089000
*             GPR14P,                                              0026 00090000
*             GPR15P)RSTD;                                         0026 00091000
*           GPR01P=SDWAPTR;                                        0027 00092000
         LR    GPR01P,SDWAPTR                                      0027 00093000
*           RESPECIFY                                              0028 00094000
*             SDWA BASED(GPR01P);                                  0028 00095000
*           SDWARCDE=0;             /* SAVE RC VALUE                 */ 00096000
         STC   @10,SDWARCDE(,GPR01P)                               0029 00097000
*           SDWARTYA=0;             /* ZERO RETRY ADDRESS FIELD      */ 00098000
         ST    @10,SDWARTYA(,GPR01P)                               0030 00099000
*           SDWARCRD='1'B;          /* TURN ON RECORD INDICATOR      */ 00100000
         OI    SDWARCRD(GPR01P),B'10000000'                        0031 00101000
*           GPR15P=ADDR(IRECM);     /* ACCESS RECORD PARAMETER LIST  */ 00102000
         LA    GPR15P,IRECM                                        0032 00103000
*           SDWAMODN=GPR15P->I256C(1:8);/* MOVE MODULE NAME INTO SDWA*/ 00104000
         MVC   SDWAMODN(8,GPR01P),I256C(GPR15P)                    0033 00105000
*           SDWACSCT=GPR15P->I256C(9:16);/* OBTAIN CSECT NAME        */ 00106000
         MVC   SDWACSCT(8,GPR01P),I256C+8(GPR15P)                  0034 00107000
*           SDWAREXN=GPR15P->I256C(17:24);/* OBTAIN FRR ID           */ 00108000
         MVC   SDWAREXN(8,GPR01P),I256C+16(GPR15P)                 0035 00109000
*           RESPECIFY                                              0036 00110000
*            (GPR00P,                                              0036 00111000
*             GPR01P,                                              0036 00112000
*             GPR14P,                                              0036 00113000
*             GPR15P)UNRSTD;                                       0036 00114000
*         END;                                                     0037 00115000
*       ELSE                                                       0038 00116000
*         DO;                       /* SETRP RECPARM(JRECM)        0038 00117000
*                                      RECORD(YES) RC(0)           0038 00118000
*                                      WKAREA(SDWAPTR)               */ 00119000
         B     @RC00024                                            0038 00120000
@RF00024 DS    0H                                                  0039 00121000
*           RESPECIFY                                              0039 00122000
*            (GPR00P,                                              0039 00123000
*             GPR01P,                                              0039 00124000
*             GPR14P,                                              0039 00125000
*             GPR15P)RSTD;                                         0039 00126000
*           GPR01P=SDWAPTR;                                        0040 00127000
         LR    GPR01P,SDWAPTR                                      0040 00128000
*           RESPECIFY                                              0041 00129000
*             SDWA BASED(GPR01P);                                  0041 00130000
*           SDWARCDE=0;             /* SAVE RC VALUE                 */ 00131000
         SR    @10,@10                                             0042 00132000
         STC   @10,SDWARCDE(,GPR01P)                               0042 00133000
*           SDWARTYA=0;             /* ZERO RETRY ADDRESS FIELD      */ 00134000
         ST    @10,SDWARTYA(,GPR01P)                               0043 00135000
*           SDWARCRD='1'B;          /* TURN ON RECORD INDICATOR      */ 00136000
         OI    SDWARCRD(GPR01P),B'10000000'                        0044 00137000
*           GPR15P=ADDR(JRECM);     /* ACCESS RECORD PARAMETER LIST  */ 00138000
         LA    GPR15P,JRECM                                        0045 00139000
*           SDWAMODN=GPR15P->I256C(1:8);/* MOVE MODULE NAME INTO SDWA*/ 00140000
         MVC   SDWAMODN(8,GPR01P),I256C(GPR15P)                    0046 00141000
*           SDWACSCT=GPR15P->I256C(9:16);/* OBTAIN CSECT NAME        */ 00142000
         MVC   SDWACSCT(8,GPR01P),I256C+8(GPR15P)                  0047 00143000
*           SDWAREXN=GPR15P->I256C(17:24);/* OBTAIN FRR ID           */ 00144000
         MVC   SDWAREXN(8,GPR01P),I256C+16(GPR15P)                 0048 00145000
*           RESPECIFY                                              0049 00146000
*            (GPR00P,                                              0049 00147000
*             GPR01P,                                              0049 00148000
*             GPR14P,                                              0049 00149000
*             GPR15P)UNRSTD;                                       0049 00150000
*         END;                                                     0050 00151000
*                                                                  0051 00152000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00153000
*       /*                                                           */ 00154000
*       /* THE PLS GOTTEN AREA MUST BE FREED ON EXIT                 */ 00155000
*       /*                                                           */ 00156000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00157000
*                                                                  0051 00158000
*       GEN;                                                       0051 00159000
@RC00024 DS    0H                                                  0051 00160000
     L   R0,@SIZDATD                                                    00161000
     FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(R11)                                          00162000
*     END;                                                         0052 00163000
*   R14=R7;                         /* RETURN ADDRESS NOW IN R14     */ 00164000
@RC00011 LR    R14,R7                                              0053 00165000
*   DECLARE                         /* GENERAL PURPOSE REGISTERS     */ 00166000
*     GPR00P PTR(31)REG(0),                                        0054 00167000
*     GPR01P PTR(31)REG(1),                                        0054 00168000

IEFI922B CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000

         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000

         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00013000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00014000
         LR    @11,@01                                             0001 00015000
         USING @DATD,@11                                           0001 00016000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00017000
         MVC   @PC00001(4),0(@01)                                  0001 00018000
*                                                                  0013 00019000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00020000
*   /*                                                               */ 00021000
*   /* BUILD A PARAMETER LIST IN LCTPARM1 THROUGH LCTPARM4 FOR       */ 00022000
*   /* IEFSD164, AS IF THE P/P HAD ABENDED WITH A 922 SYSTEM         */ 00023000
*   /* COMPLETION CODE.                                              */ 00024000
*   /*                                                               */ 00025000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00026000
*                                                                  0013 00027000
*   PARM1A=TCBFABIT;                /* SET BIT INDICATING THIS IS AN    00028000
*                                      ABEND CODE (NOT A REG 15    0013 00029000
*                                      RETURN CODE)                  */ 00030000
         L     @10,@PC00001                                        0013 00031000
         L     @10,PARAMPTR(,@10)                                  0013 00032000
         L     @15,IEFLCTAD(,@10)                                  0013 00033000
         MVI   PARM1A(@15),X'80'                                   0013 00034000
*   PARM1BCD=TCBTCTB;               /* PASS TCT POINTER              */ 00035000
         L     @14,LCTTCBAD(,@15)                                  0014 00036000
         MVC   PARM1BCD(3,@15),TCBTCTB(@14)                        0014 00037000
*   PARM3A=TCBDSP;                  /* PASS TCB PRIORITY             */ 00038000
         MVC   PARM3A(1,@15),TCBDSP(@14)                           0015 00039000
*   LCTPARM4=CODE922;               /* PASS COMPLETION CODE          */ 00040000

*   LCTADDR=ADDR(LCT);              /* LCT POINTER IS REQUIRED IN  0017 00042000
*                                      FIRST WORD BY IEFSD164        */ 00043000
         ST    @15,LCTADDR(,@10)                                   0017 00044000
*   END                                                            0018 00045000

./  ADD  SSI=32180935,NAME=IEFJACTL
         TITLE 'IEFJACTL - PSEUDO ACCESS METHOD ACCESS METHOD CONTROL  *00001000
                       '                                                00002000
IEFJACTL CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IEFJACTL  73.218'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00014000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00015000
         LR    @11,@01                                             0001 00016000
         USING @DATD,@11                                           0001 00017000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00018000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00019000
         ST    @11,8(,@13)                                         0001 00020000
         LR    @13,@11                                             0001 00021000
*                                                                  0038 00022000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00023000
*   /*                                                               */ 00024000
*   /* SET UP BASED VARIABLES                                        */ 00025000
*   /*                                                               */ 00026000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00027000
*                                                                  0038 00028000
*   RPLPTR=R1;                      /* SAVE THE POINTER TO THE RPL   */ 00029000
         LR    RPLPTR,R1                                           0038 00030000
*   RFY                                                            0039 00031000
*     IFGRPL BASED(RPLPTR);         /* THE RPL MACRO IS BASED ON   0039 00032000
*                                      RPLPTR                        */ 00033000
*   RFY                                                            0040 00034000
*     IFGACB BASED(RPLDACB);        /* THE ACB IS BASED ON A PTR IN     00035000
*                                      THE RPL                       */ 00036000
*   RFY                                                            0041 00037000
*     ACBPRFIX BASED(ADDR(IFGACB)-4);/* GET THE ACB PREFIX           */ 00038000
*   RFY                                                            0042 00039000
*     IEFJAMWD BASED(ACBPRFIX);     /* THE ACCESS METHOD WORK AREA IS   00040000
*                                      BASED ON THE ACB PREFIX       */ 00041000
*                                                                  0042 00042000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00043000
*   /*                                                               */ 00044000
*   /* CHECK RPLPTR                                                  */ 00045000
*   /*                                                               */ 00046000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00047000
*                                                                  0043 00048000
*   IF RPLPTR=0 THEN                /* CHECK RPLPTR IF =0 ISSUE ABEND*/ 00049000
         LTR   RPLPTR,RPLPTR                                       0043 00050000
         BNZ   @RF00043                                            0043 00051000
*     GEN(ABEND 177,,,SYSTEM);                                     0044 00052000
*                                                                  0044 00053000
         ABEND 177,,,SYSTEM                                             00054000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00055000
*   /*                                                               */ 00056000
*   /* TEST THE BITS IN THE RPL AND PERFORM THE OPERATION REQUESTED  */ 00057000
*   /*                                                               */ 00058000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00059000
*                                                                  0045 00060000
*   R1=RPLPTR;                      /* MAKE SURE THAT R1 POINTS TO 0045 00061000
*                                      THE RPL                       */ 00062000
@RF00043 LR    R1,RPLPTR                                           0045 00063000
*   RETCD=0;                        /* SET ZERO RETURN CODE          */ 00064000
         SR    RETCD,RETCD                                         0046 00065000
*   IF(RPLREQ=0)&(RPLDIR='1'B)&(RPLUPD='1'B)THEN                   0047 00066000
         CLI   RPLREQ(RPLPTR),0                                    0047 00067000
         BNE   @RF00047                                            0047 00068000
         TM    RPLDIR(RPLPTR),B'01000000'                          0047 00069000
         BNO   @RF00047                                            0047 00070000
         TM    RPLUPD(RPLPTR),B'00000010'                          0047 00071000
         BNO   @RF00047                                            0047 00072000
*     CALL IEFJDIRD;                /* CALL DIRECT READ              */ 00073000
         L     @15,@CV00045                                        0048 00074000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0048 00075000
*   ELSE                                                           0049 00076000
*     IF(RPLREQ=0)&(RPLSEQ='1'B)THEN                               0049 00077000
         B     @RC00047                                            0049 00078000
@RF00047 CLI   RPLREQ(RPLPTR),0                                    0049 00079000
         BNE   @RF00049                                            0049 00080000
         TM    RPLSEQ(RPLPTR),B'00100000'                          0049 00081000
         BNO   @RF00049                                            0049 00082000
*       IF AMWDEOF=ON THEN          /* TEST FOR EOF SET UP BY A PRIOR   00083000
*                                      OPERATION                     */ 00084000
         L     @10,RPLDACB(,RPLPTR)                                0050 00085000
         AL    @10,@CF00334                                        0050 00086000
         L     @10,ACBPRFIX(,@10)                                  0050 00087000
         TM    AMWDEOF(@10),B'10000000'                            0050 00088000
         BNO   @RF00050                                            0050 00089000
*         DO;                       /* IF ON THEN SET UP THE BITS IN    00090000
*                                      THE RPL                       */ 00091000
*           RPLRTNCD=8;             /* RPL RETURN CODE               */ 00092000
         MVI   RPLRTNCD(RPLPTR),X'08'                              0052 00093000
*           RETCD=8;                /* SET RETURN CODE = 8           */ 00094000
         LA    RETCD,8                                             0053 00095000
*           RPLERRCD=RPLEODER;      /* NO EOD ADDRESS                */ 00096000
         MVI   RPLERRCD(RPLPTR),X'04'                              0054 00097000
*         END;                                                     0055 00098000
*       ELSE                                                       0056 00099000
*         CALL IEFJREAD;            /* REQUEST IS FOR A SEQUENTIAL 0056 00100000
*                                      READ                          */ 00101000
         B     @RC00050                                            0056 00102000
@RF00050 L     @15,@CV00047                                        0056 00103000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0056 00104000
*     ELSE                                                         0057 00105000
*       IF(RPLREQ=1)&(RPLDIR='1'B)&(RPLUPD='1'B)THEN               0057 00106000
         B     @RC00049                                            0057 00107000
@RF00049 CLI   RPLREQ(RPLPTR),1                                    0057 00108000
         BNE   @RF00057                                            0057 00109000

         BNO   @RF00057                                            0057 00111000

         L     @15,@CV00046                                        0058 00115000

         ABEND 179,,,SYSTEM                                             00132000
