         TITLE 'I E F J C D L T - CORE DELETION                      '  00001000
IEFJCDLT CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IEFJCDLT  73.059'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00013000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00014000
         LR    @11,@01                                             0001 00015000
         USING @DATD,@11                                           0001 00016000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00017000
         XC    @ZTEMPS(@ZLEN),@ZTEMPS                                   00018000
         MVC   @PC00001(4),0(@01)                                  0001 00019000
*   AMWAPTR=INPUT1;                 /* PTR INITIALIZED FOR AMWA      */ 00020000
         L     @10,@PC00001                                        0005 00021000
         L     AMWAPTR,INPUT1(,@10)                                0005 00022000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0006 00023000
*     IEFJAREA BASED(ADDRAREA);                                    0006 00024000
*   IF AMWAPTR¬=0 THEN              /* VALIDITY CHECK PARM FIELD. A     00025000
*                                      ZERO SIGNALS THAT CANNOT FREE    00026000
*                                      JCLS CHAIN.                   */ 00027000
*                                                                  0007 00028000
         LTR   AMWAPTR,AMWAPTR                                     0007 00029000
         BZ    @RF00007                                            0007 00030000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00031000
*     /*                                                             */ 00032000
*     /* FREE JCLS CHAIN                                             */ 00033000
*     /*                                                             */ 00034000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00035000
*                                                                  0008 00036000
*JCDLT010:                                                         0008 00037000
*     DO WHILE AMWAFSTJ¬=0;         /* LOOP TO FREE JCLS CHAIN       */ 00038000
JCDLT010 B     @DE00008                                            0008 00039000
@DL00008 DS    0H                                                  0009 00040000
*       ADDRAREA=AMWAFSTJ;          /* ADDRESS OF RECORD TO FREE     */ 00041000
         L     @10,AMWAFSTJ(,AMWAPTR)                              0009 00042000
         ST    @10,ADDRAREA                                        0009 00043000
*       AREALEN=JCLSLEN;            /* LENGTH OF RECORD TO FREE      */ 00044000
         MVC   AREALEN(3),@CF00084+1                               0010 00045000
*       AMWAFSTJ=NEXTPTR;           /* RESET TO POINT TO NEXT CHAIN     00046000
*                                      ELEMENT                       */ 00047000
         MVC   AMWAFSTJ(4,AMWAPTR),NEXTPTR(@10)                    0011 00048000
*       SPNUM=JSUBPOOL;             /* SUBPOOL WHERE CHAIN OF JCLS 0012 00049000
*                                      RESIDES.(253)                 */ 00050000
         MVI   SPNUM,X'FD'                                         0012 00051000
*       REG1=ADDRAREA;              /* REGISTER 1 POINTS TO AREA TO     00052000
*                                      BE FREED.                     */ 00053000
         LR    REG1,@10                                            0013 00054000
*       REG0=SPLEN;                 /* REGISTER 0 CONTAINS SUBPOOL 0014 00055000
*                                      NUMBER IN HIGH ORDER BYTE, AND   00056000
*                                      LENGTH IN LAST 3              */ 00057000
         L     REG0,SPLEN                                          0014 00058000
*       GEN(FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1));/* FREE ELEMENT IN CHAIN.       */ 00059000
         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00060000
*     END JCDLT010;                                                0016 00061000
*                                                                  0016 00062000
@DE00008 L     @10,AMWAFSTJ(,AMWAPTR)                              0016 00063000
         LTR   @10,@10                                             0016 00064000
         BNZ   @DL00008                                            0016 00065000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00066000
*   /*                                                               */ 00067000
*   /* FREE SUBPOOL 10                                               */ 00068000
*   /*                                                               */ 00069000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00070000
*                                                                  0017 00071000
*   GEN(FREEMAIN R,SP=10);                                         0017 00072000
*                                                                  0017 00073000
@RF00007 DS    0H                                                  0017 00074000
         FREEMAIN R,SP=10                                               00075000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00076000
*   /*                                                               */ 00077000
*   /* RETURN RETURN WITHOUT RETURN CODE                             */ 00078000
*   /*                                                               */ 00079000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00080000
*                                                                  0018 00081000
*   RETURN;                                                        0018 00082000
@EL00001 DS    0H                                                  0018 00083000

         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00086000

         ST    @14,ATACHECB                                        0144 00482000
*       REG15=ADDR(CONATCHD);       /* ADDRESS OF ATTACH LIST        */ 00483000
         LA    REG15,CONATCHD                                      0145 00484000
*       RESPECIFY                                                  0146 00485000
*         REG8 RSTD;                                               0146 00486000
*       GEN;                                                       0147 00487000
         ATTACH  EP=IEFVH1,ECB=(7),SHSPV=10,SF=(E,(15))                 00488000
*       IF REG15¬=0 THEN            /* IF ATTACH WAS NOT SUCCESSFUL  */ 00489000
         LTR   REG15,REG15                                         0148 00490000
         BZ    @RF00148                                            0148 00491000
*         DO;                                                      0149 00492000
*           GEN(ABEND 181,,,SYSTEM);/* ISSUE 0B5 ABEND               */ 00493000
         ABEND 181,,,SYSTEM                                             00494000
*         END;                                                     0151 00495000
*       CONVRTCB=REG1;              /* ADDRESS OF CONVERTER TCB      */ 00496000
@RF00148 ST    REG1,CONVRTCB                                       0152 00497000
*       GEN;                                                       0153 00498000
*                                                                  0153 00499000
*                       /*WAIT FOR CONVERTER SUBTASK TO TERMINATE*/     00500000
         WAIT    1,ECB=(7)                                              00501000
         DETACH CONVRTCB                                                00502000
*/* RETURN CODE PASSED BACK FROM CONVERTER IN ATTACH ECB             */ 00503000
*                                                                  0154 00504000
*       IF COMPCODE¬=0 THEN         /* NON ZERO RETURN CODE FROM   0154 00505000
*                                      CONVERTER SIGNALS TROUBLE     */ 00506000
         ICM   @14,7,COMPCODE                                      0154 00507000
         BZ    @RF00154                                            0154 00508000
*JCNTL080:                                                         0155 00509000
*         DO;                                                      0155 00510000
*                                                                  0155 00511000
JCNTL080 DS    0H                                                  0156 00512000
*/* A TEST MUST BE MADE TO DETERMINE IF THE RETURN CODE IS ACTUALLY     00513000
*   AN ABEND CODE.THE BITS 8-19 OF THE ECB ARE MASKED OUT.IF THE   0156 00514000
*   TEST OF THE RETURN CODE NOW SHOWS A ZERO,IT WAS AN ABEND CODE  0156 00515000
*   IN THE ECB.IN THIS CASE, A RETURN CODE OF 36 IS PLACED INTO    0156 00516000
*   SSOB AND THE BYPASS INTERPRETER SWITCH IS TURNED ON.IF NOT     0156 00517000
*   AN ABEND,RETURN CODE TESTS ARE PERFORMED.                        */ 00518000
*                                                                  0156 00519000
*           COMPCODE=COMPCODE&ABENDMSK;/* MASK OUT ABEND CODE        */ 00520000
         SLR   @14,@14                                             0156 00521000
         ICM   @14,7,COMPCODE                                      0156 00522000
         SLR   @10,@10                                             0156 00523000
         ICM   @10,7,ABENDMSK                                      0156 00524000
         NR    @14,@10                                             0156 00525000
         STCM  @14,7,COMPCODE                                      0156 00526000
*           IF COMPCODE=0 THEN      /* IF COMPCODE IS NOW ZERO IT WAS   00527000
*                                      AN ABEND.                     */ 00528000
         LTR   @14,@14                                             0157 00529000
         BNZ   @RF00157                                            0157 00530000
*             DO;                                                  0158 00531000
*               SSJSSERR=SSJSPERR;  /* PUT 36 INTO RETURN CODE FLD   */ 00532000
         L     @14,SSOBINDV(,SSOBPTR)                              0159 00533000
         MVC   SSJSSERR(4,@14),@CF00064                            0159 00534000
*               BYPINTER=ON;        /* BYPASS GOING TO INTERPRETER   */ 00535000
         OI    BYPINTER(AMWAPTR),B'01000000'                       0160 00536000
*             END;                                                 0161 00537000
*           ELSE                                                   0162 00538000
*             DO;                                                  0162 00539000
         B     @RC00157                                            0162 00540000
@RF00157 DS    0H                                                  0163 00541000
*               SSJSSERR=COMPCODE;  /* RETURN CODE TO SSOB AS IS     */ 00542000
         SLR   @14,@14                                             0163 00543000
         ICM   @14,7,COMPCODE                                      0163 00544000
         L     @10,SSOBINDV(,SSOBPTR)                              0163 00545000
         ST    @14,SSJSSERR(,@10)                                  0163 00546000
*               IF COMPCODE=4 THEN  /* FOUR IS A JCL ERROR           */ 00547000
         CH    @14,@CH00039                                        0164 00548000
         BNE   @RF00164                                            0164 00549000
*                 CONVERR=ON;       /* TURN ON CONV.ERR SW.          */ 00550000
         OI    CONVERR(AMWAPTR),B'10000000'                        0165 00551000
*               ELSE                                               0166 00552000
*                                                                  0166 00553000
*/* ANYTHING OTHER THAN A RETURN CODE OF 4 IS A TERMINATING SITUATION.  00554000
*   TURN ON THE BYPASS INTERPRETER CODE AND CONTINUE PROCESSING.     */ 00555000
*                                                                  0166 00556000
*                 BYPINTER=ON;      /* BYPASS INTERPRETER            */ 00557000
         B     @RC00164                                            0166 00558000
@RF00164 OI    BYPINTER(AMWAPTR),B'01000000'                       0166 00559000
*             END;                                                 0167 00560000
@RC00164 DS    0H                                                  0168 00561000
*         END JCNTL080;                                            0168 00562000
@RC00157 DS    0H                                                  0169 00563000
*       IF SSIBSUSE¬=0 THEN         /* IF MSTR NOT STARTED THEN CLOSE   00564000
*                                      PROCLIB                       */ 00565000
@RF00154 L     @14,SSIBPTR                                         0169 00566000
         ICM   @10,15,SSIBSUSE(@14)                                0169 00567000
         BZ    @RF00169                                            0169 00568000
*JCNTL090:                                                         0170 00569000
*         DO;                                                      0170 00570000
JCNTL090 DS    0H                                                  0171 00571000
*           REG7=ADDR(PROCOPND);    /* PTR TO PROC LIST              */ 00572000
         LA    REG7,PROCOPND                                       0171 00573000
*           REG8=NELPROCB;          /* ADDRESS OF PROCLIB DCB        */ 00574000
         L     REG8,NELPROCB(,NELPTR)                              0172 00575000
*           GEN(CLOSE ((8)),MF=(E,(7)));/* CLOSE PROCLIB             */ 00576000
         CLOSE ((8)),MF=(E,(7))                                         00577000
*         END JCNTL090;                                            0174 00578000
*                                                                  0175 00579000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00580000
*       /*                                                           */ 00581000
*       /* SETUP FOR SWA CREATE                                      */ 00582000
*       /*                                                           */ 00583000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00584000
*                                                                  0175 00585000
*       IF BYPINTER¬=ON THEN        /* GIVE CONTROL TO INTERPRETER   */ 00586000
*                                                                  0175 00587000
@RF00169 TM    BYPINTER(AMWAPTR),B'01000000'                       0175 00588000
         BO    @RF00175                                            0175 00589000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00590000
*         /*                                                         */ 00591000
*         /* RESET TEXT ENTRY IN AMWA                                */ 00592000
*         /*                                                         */ 00593000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00594000
*                                                                  0176 00595000
*/*  SET UP TO ALLOW READING FROM TEXT STRING FROM FIRST RECORD.     */ 00596000
*                                                                  0176 00597000
*JCNTL0A0:                                                         0176 00598000
*         DO;                                                      0176 00599000
JCNTL0A0 DS    0H                                                  0177 00600000
*           AMWALSTT=AMWAFSTT;                                     0177 00601000
*                                                                  0177 00602000
         MVC   AMWALSTT(4,AMWAPTR),AMWAFSTT(AMWAPTR)               0177 00603000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00604000
*           /*                                                       */ 00605000
*           /* S S O B                                               */ 00606000
*           /*                                                       */ 00607000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00608000
*                                                                  0178 00609000
*           SSJSMACB=NELMSGCB;      /* MSG ACB PTR INTO SSOB         */ 00610000

*           SSJSJACB=0;             /* ZERO JOURNAL ACB PTR          */ 00613000

*           SSJSJMR=0;              /* JMR POINTER ZEROED            */ 00616000

         MVC   SSJSTACB(4,@14),NELTXTCB(NELPTR)                    0181 00619000

*                                                                  0182 00621000
*           REG1=SSOBPTR;                                          0182 00622000
         LR    REG1,SSOBPTR                                        0182 00623000
*           GEN(LINK EP=IEFIB600);                                 0183 00624000
*                                                                  0183 00625000
         LINK EP=IEFIB600                                               00626000
*/*RETURN CODE FROM SWA CREATE WILL BE PASSED IN REGISTER 15.      0184 00627000
*  ANYTHING OTHER THAN ZERO IS AN ERROR CONDITION AND REQUIRES     0184 00628000
* THAT THE VALUE IN REGISTER 15 BE PUT INTO THE SSOB ALONG WITH A  0184 00629000
* RETURN CODE FOR THE INITIATOR.IF THE CONVERTER HAS ALREADY FOUND 0184 00630000
* AN ERROR,THIS RETURN CODE WILL NOT OVERLAY THE CONVERTER ERROR   0184 00631000
* CODES.IF REGISTER 15 IS ZERO,NO CODE IS PLACED INTO THE SSOB.      */ 00632000
*                                                                  0184 00633000
*           IF CONVERR=OFF THEN     /* NO CONVERTER ERRORS           */ 00634000
         TM    CONVERR(AMWAPTR),B'10000000'                        0184 00635000
         BNZ   @RF00184                                            0184 00636000
*             DO;                                                  0185 00637000
*               IF REG15¬=0 THEN                                   0186 00638000

*                   SSOBRETN=SSJSYSER;/* RETURN CODE IN SSOB         */ 00645000
         MVC   SSOBRETN(4,SSOBPTR),@CF00055                        0189 00646000
*                 END;                                             0190 00647000
*             END;                                                 0191 00648000

*         END JCNTL0A0;                                            0193 00653000
*       ELSE                                                       0194 00654000
*         SSOBRETN=SSJSYSER;        /* SIGNAL INITIATOR TO STOP.   0194 00655000
*                                      THERE IS NO TASK TO INITIATE  */ 00656000
         B     @RC00175                                            0194 00657000
@RF00175 MVC   SSOBRETN(4,SSOBPTR),@CF00055                        0194 00658000
*     END JCNTL010;                                                0195 00659000

*   /*****************************************************************/ 00661000
*   /*                                                               */ 00662000
*   /* RETURN TO CALLER                                              */ 00663000
*   /*                                                               */ 00664000

@EL00001 L     @13,4(,@13)                                         0196 00668000

@RF00137 EQU   @RC00127                                                 02383000

./  ADD  SSI=30192418,NAME=IEFJDIRD
         TITLE 'IEFJDIRD - PSEUDO ACCESS METHOD PERFORM A DIRECT READ'  00001000
IEFJDIRD CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IEFJDIRD  73.020'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
*                                                                  0004 00013000
*/*         PHYSICAL ERROR CONDITIONS (REGISTER 15 = 12)             */ 00014000
*/*      SET UP BASED VARIABLES                                      */ 00015000
*                                                                  0005 00016000
*   RPLPTR=R1;                      /* SAVE THE POINTER IN R1 POINTS    00017000
*                                      TO THE RPL                    */ 00018000
         LR    RPLPTR,R1                                           0005 00019000
*   RFY                                                            0006 00020000
*     IFGRPL BASED(RPLPTR);         /* THE RPL IS BASED ON CONTENTS     00021000
*                                      OF RPLPTR                     */ 00022000
*   RFY                                                            0007 00023000
*     IEFJAREA BASED(RPLDDDP-8);    /* POINT TO THE BEGINNING OF THE    00024000
*                                      RECORD                        */ 00025000
*                                                                  0007 00026000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00027000
*   /*                                                               */ 00028000
*   /* PERFORM A DIRECT READ                                         */ 00029000
*   /*                                                               */ 00030000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00031000
*                                                                  0008 00032000
*   NEWLGTH=LGTH-8;                 /* GET THE LGTH OF THE TEXT ONLY */ 00033000
         LA    @10,8                                               0008 00034000
         L     @07,RPLARG(,RPLPTR)                                 0008 00035000
         L     @07,RPLDDDP(,@07)                                   0008 00036000
         SR    @07,@10                                             0008 00037000
         LCR   @10,@10                                             0008 00038000
         A     @10,LGTH(,@07)                                      0008 00039000
         LR    NEWLGTH,@10                                         0008 00040000
*   TEXTPTR=RPLAREA;                /* TEXTPTR NOW POINTS TO THE AREA   00041000
*                                      THAT THE REC WILL BE READ INTO*/ 00042000
         L     TEXTPTR,RPLAREA(,RPLPTR)                            0009 00043000
*   RECPTR=ADDR(IEFJAREA);          /* RECPTR POINTS TO THE REC TO BE   00044000
*                                      READ                          */ 00045000
         LR    RECPTR,@07                                          0010 00046000
*   IF NEWLGTH<=256 THEN            /* CHECK LENGTH OF REC IF > 256     00047000
*                                      MORE THAN ONE MOVE IS       0011 00048000
*                                      NECESSARY                     */ 00049000
         CH    NEWLGTH,@CH00134                                    0011 00050000
         BH    @RF00011                                            0011 00051000
*     TEXTAREA(1:NEWLGTH)=RECTEXT(1:NEWLGTH);/* LESS THAN 256 MOVE 0012 00052000
*                                      AND END                       */ 00053000
         LR    @10,NEWLGTH                                         0012 00054000
         BCTR  @10,0                                               0012 00055000
         EX    @10,@SM00136                                        0012 00056000
*   ELSE                                                           0013 00057000
*     DO;                                                          0013 00058000
         B     @RC00011                                            0013 00059000
@RF00011 DS    0H                                                  0014 00060000
*       CTR=NEWLGTH/256;            /* SET CTR TO THE NUMBER OF MOVES   00061000
*                                      NECESSARY                     */ 00062000
         LR    @08,NEWLGTH                                         0014 00063000
         SRDA  @08,32                                              0014 00064000
         D     @08,@CF00134                                        0014 00065000
         LR    CTR,@09                                             0014 00066000
*       DO WHILE CTR>0;             /* EXECUTE UNTIL ALL 256 BYTE  0015 00067000
*                                      BLOCKS HAVE BEEN MOVED        */ 00068000
         B     @DE00015                                            0015 00069000
@DL00015 DS    0H                                                  0016 00070000
*         TEXTAREA(1:256)=RECPTR->RECTEXT(1:256);/* MOVE 256 BYTES AT   00071000
*                                      A TIME                        */ 00072000
         MVC   TEXTAREA(256,TEXTPTR),RECTEXT(RECPTR)               0016 00073000
*         TEXTPTR=TEXTPTR+256;      /* UPDATE POINTER                */ 00074000
         LA    @10,256                                             0017 00075000
         AR    TEXTPTR,@10                                         0017 00076000
*         RECPTR=RECPTR+256;        /* UPDATE POINTER                */ 00077000
         AR    RECPTR,@10                                          0018 00078000
*         CTR=CTR-1;                /* DECREMENT COUNTER             */ 00079000
         BCTR  CTR,0                                               0019 00080000
*       END;                                                       0020 00081000
@DE00015 LTR   CTR,CTR                                             0020 00082000
         BP    @DL00015                                            0020 00083000
*       CTR=NEWLGTH//256;           /* SET REMAINING LENGTH IN CTR   */ 00084000
         LR    CTR,NEWLGTH                                         0021 00085000
         N     CTR,@CF00138                                        0021 00086000
*       TEXTAREA(1:CTR)=RECPTR->RECTEXT(1:CTR);/* MOVE REMAINING   0022 00087000
*                                      LENGTH                        */ 00088000
         LR    @10,CTR                                             0022 00089000
         BCTR  @10,0                                               0022 00090000
         EX    @10,@SM00139                                        0022 00091000
*     END;                                                         0023 00092000
*   RPLDDDD=RPLDDDP;                /* RETURN THE ADDR OF THE RECORD    00093000
*                                      MOVED                         */ 00094000
@RC00011 L     @10,RPLARG(,RPLPTR)                                 0024 00095000
         MVC   RPLDDDD(4,RPLPTR),RPLDDDP(@10)                      0024 00096000
*   END IEFJDIRD                    /* RETURN TO THE CALLER          */ 00097000
*                                                                  0025 00098000
*/* THE FOLLOWING INCLUDE STATEMENTS WERE FOUND IN THIS PROGRAM.     */ 00099000
*/*%INCLUDE SYSLIB  (IEFJAREA)                                       */ 00100000
*/*%INCLUDE SYSLIB  (IFGRPL  )                                       */ 00101000
*                                                                  0025 00102000
*       ;                                                          0025 00103000
@EL00001 DS    0H                                                  0025 00104000
@EF00001 DS    0H                                                  0025 00105000
@ER00001 LM    @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0025 00106000
         BR    @14                                                 0025 00107000
@DATA    DS    0H                                                       00108000
@SM00136 MVC   TEXTAREA(0,TEXTPTR),RECTEXT(@07)                         00109000
@SM00139 MVC   TEXTAREA(0,TEXTPTR),RECTEXT(RECPTR)                      00110000
@DATD    DSECT                                                          00111000
         DS    0F                                                       00112000
IEFJDIRD CSECT                                                          00113000
         DS    0F                                                       00114000
@CF00138 DC    F'255'                                                   00115000
@CF00134 DC    F'256'                                                   00116000
@CH00134 EQU   @CF00134+2                                               00117000
@DATD    DSECT                                                          00118000
         DS    0D                                                       00119000
@ENDDATD EQU   *                                                        00120000
IEFJDIRD CSECT                                                          00121000
         NOPR  ((@ENDDATD-@DATD)*16)                                    00122000
         DS    0F                                                       00123000
@SIZDATD DC    AL1(0)                                                   00124000
         DC    AL3(@ENDDATD-@DATD)                                      00125000
         DS    0D                                                       00126000
PTCHDIRD DC    X'00'                                                    00127000
         DS    9XL1                                                     00128000
@00      EQU   00                      EQUATES FOR REGISTERS 0-15       00129000
@01      EQU   01                                                       00130000

./  ADD  SSI=40101625,NAME=IEFJDSNA
         TITLE 'IEFJDSNA-DSNAME ALLOCATION                             *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IEFJDSNA CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IEFJDSNA  74.010'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
*                                                                    */ 00014000
*                                                                  0040 00015000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00016000
*   /*                                                               */ 00017000
*   /* THE FOLLOWING CODE BUILDS A 44 CHARACTER DSNAME IN THE FORMAT */ 00018000
*   /* SPECIFIED IN THE PROLOGUE                                     */ 00019000
*   /*                                                               */ 00020000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00021000
*                                                                  0040 00022000
*   IF(SSOBINDV¬=0)&(SSALSSNM¬=0)&(SSALJFCB¬=0)&(SSALDDNM¬=0) THEN 0040 00023000
         SLR   @15,@15                                             0040 00024000
         L     @14,SSOBINDV(,SSOBPTR)                              0040 00025000
         CR    @14,@15                                             0040 00026000
         BE    @RF00040                                            0040 00027000
         L     @11,SSALSSNM(,@14)                                  0040 00028000
         CR    @11,@15                                             0040 00029000
         BE    @RF00040                                            0040 00030000
         L     @10,SSALJFCB(,@14)                                  0040 00031000
         CR    @10,@15                                             0040 00032000
         BE    @RF00040                                            0040 00033000
         L     @14,SSALDDNM(,@14)                                  0040 00034000
         CR    @14,@15                                             0040 00035000
         BE    @RF00040                                            0040 00036000
*     DO;                           /* IF THE PTR TO THE DDNAME,THE     00037000
*                                      PTR TO THE SSOB ALLOCATION  0041 00038000
*                                      FUNCTIONAL SECTION,THE PTR TO    00039000
*                                      THE SUBSYSTEM NAME, AND THE 0041 00040000
*                                      PTR TO THE JFCB ARE NOT ZERO     00041000
*                                      THEN PROCESS THE REQUEST      */ 00042000
*       JFCBDSNM=' ';               /* INITIALIZE THE DSNAME TO    0042 00043000
*                                      BLANKS                        */ 00044000
         MVI   JFCBDSNM+1(@10),C' '                                0042 00045000
         MVC   JFCBDSNM+2(42,@10),JFCBDSNM+1(@10)                  0042 00046000
         MVI   JFCBDSNM(@10),C' '                                  0042 00047000
*       XXXX=JESPJESN;              /* INSERT THE PRIMARY SUBSYSTEM     00048000
*                                      NAME                          */ 00049000
         L     @09,CVTPTR                                          0043 00050000
         L     @09,CVTJESCT(,@09)                                  0043 00051000
         MVC   XXXX(4,@10),JESPJESN(@09)                           0043 00052000
*       SUBSYNM=JESPJESN;           /* PUT THE PRIMARY SUBSYSTEM NAME   00053000
*                                      IN THE DSAB                   */ 00054000
         MVC   SUBSYNM(4,@11),JESPJESN(@09)                        0044 00055000
*       DOT1=DOT;                   /* INDERT A LEVEL DELIMETER      */ 00056000
         MVC   DOT1(1,@10),DOT                                     0045 00057000
*       YYYYYYYY=SSIBJBID;          /* INSERT THE JOBID              */ 00058000
         L     @11,SSOBSSIB(,SSOBPTR)                              0046 00059000
         MVC   YYYYYYYY(8,@10),SSIBJBID(@11)                       0046 00060000
*       DOT2=DOT;                   /* INSERT THE LEVEL DELIMETER    */ 00061000
         MVC   DOT2(1,@10),DOT                                     0047 00062000
*       AAZZZZ=DSID;                /* INSERT THE DATA SET ID        */ 00063000
         MVC   AAZZZZ(6,@10),DSID                                  0048 00064000
*       DOT3=DOT;                   /* INSERT THE LEVEL DELIMETER    */ 00065000
         MVC   DOT3(1,@10),DOT                                     0049 00066000
*       BBBBBBBB=SSOBDDNM;          /* INSERT THE DDNAME             */ 00067000
         MVC   BBBBBBBB(8,@10),SSOBDDNM(@14)                       0050 00068000
*       SSOBRETN=SSALRTOK;          /* INDICATE DSNAME ASSIGNED      */ 00069000
         ST    @15,SSOBRETN(,SSOBPTR)                              0051 00070000
*     END;                                                         0052 00071000
*   ELSE                                                           0053 00072000
*     SSOBRETN=SSALUNAL;            /* INDICATE ALLOCATION         0053 00073000
*                                      UNSUCCESSFUL          @YM04976*/ 00074000
         B     @RC00040                                            0053 00075000
@RF00040 MVC   SSOBRETN(4,SSOBPTR),@CF00046                        0053 00076000
*   RETURN CODE(SSRTOK);            /* RETURN TO THE CALLER          */ 00077000
@RC00040 SLR   @15,@15                                             0054 00078000
         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0054 00079000

./  ADD  SSI=30192419,NAME=IEFJDWRT
         TITLE 'IEFJDWRT - PSEUDO ACCESS METHOD PERFORM A DIRECT WRIT'  00001000
IEFJDWRT CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IEFJDWRT  73.020'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
*                                                                  0004 00013000
*/*         PHYSICAL ERROR CONDITIONS (REGISTER 15 = 12)             */ 00014000
*/*     SET UP BASED VARIABLES                                       */ 00015000
*                                                                  0005 00016000
*   RPLPTR=R1;                      /* SAVE THE POINTER IN R1 POINTS    00017000
*                                      TO THE RPL                    */ 00018000
         LR    RPLPTR,R1                                           0005 00019000
*   RFY                                                            0006 00020000
*     IFGRPL BASED(RPLPTR);         /* THE RPL IS BASED ON CONTENTS     00021000
*                                      OF RPLPTR                     */ 00022000
*   RFY                                                            0007 00023000
*     IEFJAREA BASED(RPLDDDP-8);    /* POINT TO THE BEGINNING OF THE    00024000
*                                      RECORD                        */ 00025000
*                                                                  0007 00026000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00027000
*   /*                                                               */ 00028000
*   /* PERFORM A DIRECT WRITE                                        */ 00029000
*   /*                                                               */ 00030000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00031000
*                                                                  0008 00032000
*   NEWLGTH=LGTH-8;                 /* GET THE LGTH OF THE TEXT ONLY */ 00033000
         LA    @10,8                                               0008 00034000
         L     @07,RPLARG(,RPLPTR)                                 0008 00035000
         L     @07,RPLDDDP(,@07)                                   0008 00036000
         SR    @07,@10                                             0008 00037000
         LCR   @10,@10                                             0008 00038000
         A     @10,LGTH(,@07)                                      0008 00039000
         LR    NEWLGTH,@10                                         0008 00040000
*   TEXTPTR=RPLAREA;                /* TEXTPTR NOW POINTS TO THE AREA   00041000
*                                      THAT THE REC WILL BE WRITTEN     00042000
*                                      FROM                          */ 00043000
         L     TEXTPTR,RPLAREA(,RPLPTR)                            0009 00044000
*   RECPTR=ADDR(IEFJAREA);          /* RECPTR POINTS TO THE REC TO BE   00045000
*                                      RE-WRITTEN                    */ 00046000
         LR    RECPTR,@07                                          0010 00047000
*   IF NEWLGTH<=256 THEN            /* CHECK LENGTH OF REC IF > 256     00048000
*                                      MORE THAN ONE MOVE IS       0011 00049000
*                                      NECESSARY                     */ 00050000
         CH    NEWLGTH,@CH00134                                    0011 00051000
         BH    @RF00011                                            0011 00052000
*     RECTEXT(1:NEWLGTH)=TEXTAREA(1:NEWLGTH);/* LESS THAN 256 MOVE 0012 00053000
*                                      AND END                       */ 00054000
         LR    @10,NEWLGTH                                         0012 00055000
         BCTR  @10,0                                               0012 00056000
         EX    @10,@SM00136                                        0012 00057000
*   ELSE                                                           0013 00058000
*     DO;                                                          0013 00059000
         B     @RC00011                                            0013 00060000
@RF00011 DS    0H                                                  0014 00061000
*       CTR=NEWLGTH/256;            /* SET CTR TO THE NUMBER OF MOVES   00062000
*                                      NECESSARY                     */ 00063000
         LR    @08,NEWLGTH                                         0014 00064000
         SRDA  @08,32                                              0014 00065000
         D     @08,@CF00134                                        0014 00066000
         LR    CTR,@09                                             0014 00067000
*       DO WHILE CTR>0;             /* EXECUTE UNTIL ALL 256 BYTE  0015 00068000
*                                      BLOCKS HAVE BEEN MOVED        */ 00069000
         B     @DE00015                                            0015 00070000
@DL00015 DS    0H                                                  0016 00071000
*         RECPTR->RECTEXT(1:256)=TEXTAREA(1:256);/* MOVE 256 BYTES AT   00072000
*                                      A TIME                        */ 00073000
         MVC   RECTEXT(256,RECPTR),TEXTAREA(TEXTPTR)               0016 00074000
*         TEXTPTR=TEXTPTR+256;      /* UPDATE POINTER                */ 00075000
         LA    @10,256                                             0017 00076000
         AR    TEXTPTR,@10                                         0017 00077000
*         RECPTR=RECPTR+256;        /* UPDATE POINTER                */ 00078000
         AR    RECPTR,@10                                          0018 00079000
*         CTR=CTR-1;                /* DECREMENT COUNTER             */ 00080000
         BCTR  CTR,0                                               0019 00081000
*       END;                                                       0020 00082000
@DE00015 LTR   CTR,CTR                                             0020 00083000
         BP    @DL00015                                            0020 00084000
*       CTR=NEWLGTH//256;           /* SET REMAINING LENGTH IN CTR   */ 00085000
         LR    CTR,NEWLGTH                                         0021 00086000
         N     CTR,@CF00138                                        0021 00087000
*       RECPTR->RECTEXT(1:CTR)=TEXTAREA(1:CTR);/* MOVE REMAINING   0022 00088000
*                                      LENGTH                        */ 00089000
         LR    @10,CTR                                             0022 00090000
         BCTR  @10,0                                               0022 00091000
         EX    @10,@SM00139                                        0022 00092000
*     END;                                                         0023 00093000
*   RPLDDDD=RPLDDDP;                /* RETURN THE ADDR OF THE RECORD    00094000
*                                      MOVED                         */ 00095000
@RC00011 L     @10,RPLARG(,RPLPTR)                                 0024 00096000
         MVC   RPLDDDD(4,RPLPTR),RPLDDDP(@10)                      0024 00097000
*   END IEFJDWRT                    /* RETURN TO THE CALLER          */ 00098000
*                                                                  0025 00099000
*/* THE FOLLOWING INCLUDE STATEMENTS WERE FOUND IN THIS PROGRAM.     */ 00100000
*/*%INCLUDE SYSLIB  (IEFJAREA)                                       */ 00101000
*/*%INCLUDE SYSLIB  (IFGRPL  )                                       */ 00102000
*                                                                  0025 00103000
*       ;                                                          0025 00104000
@EL00001 DS    0H                                                  0025 00105000
@EF00001 DS    0H                                                  0025 00106000
@ER00001 LM    @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0025 00107000
         BR    @14                                                 0025 00108000
@DATA    DS    0H                                                       00109000
@SM00136 MVC   RECTEXT(0,@07),TEXTAREA(TEXTPTR)                         00110000
@SM00139 MVC   RECTEXT(0,RECPTR),TEXTAREA(TEXTPTR)                      00111000
@DATD    DSECT                                                          00112000
         DS    0F                                                       00113000

*                                                                  0003 00019000

*           GEN(DELETE EP=MSTRJCL);                                0047 00136000
         DELETE EP=MSTRJCL                                              00137000
*         END JJOBS030;                                            0048 00138000

*JJOBS050:                                                         0049 00140000
*         DO;                                                      0049 00141000

@RF00031 DS    0H                                                  0049 00143000

*         END JJOBS050;                                            0052 00152000
*                                                                  0052 00153000
*/*                 SINCE JCLS HAS NO LENGTH INDICATOR LIKE THE OTHER   00154000
*                   RECORDS THE ACCESS METHOD WILL READ,A BIT HAS  0053 00155000
*                   TO SIGNAL THAT 80 BYTES MUST BE MOVED.EVERY ENTRY   00156000

*       /*                                                           */ 00165000
*       /* SETUP FOR IEFJCNTL                                        */ 00166000

*                                                                  0054 00169000

*       /*************************************************************/ 00194000
*       /*                                                           */ 00195000

*       /* CHAIN                                                     */ 00197000
*       /*                                                           */ 00198000

*   /* RETURNED ZEROED.                                              */ 00215000

./  ADD  SSI=30611819,NAME=IEFJJTRM
         TITLE 'IEFJJTRM-SUBSYSTEM JOB TERMINATION                   '  00001000
IEFJJTRM CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IEFJJTRM  73.062'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
*                                                                  0027 00013000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00014000
*   /*                                                               */ 00015000
*   /* NOTE- THIS MODULE ONLY PERFORMS JOB TERMINATION SERVICES FOR  */ 00016000
*   /* SUBSYSTEMS. THESE SERVICES ARE SIMPLY A RETURN TO THE CALLER  */ 00017000
*   /* WITH CONDITIONS CODES SET TO ZERO TO ALLOW THE TASK TO        */ 00018000
*   /* TERMINATE WITHOUT ABENDING.                                   */ 00019000
*   /*                                                               */ 00020000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00021000
*                                                                  0027 00022000
*   SSCVTPTR=JESSSCT;               /* GET ADDR OF FIRST SSCVT       */ 00023000
         L     @15,CVTPTR                                          0027 00024000
         L     @15,CVTJESCT(,@15)                                  0027 00025000
         L     SSCVTPTR,JESSSCT(,@15)                              0027 00026000
*   SSOBRETN=0;                     /* INITIALIZE SSOBRETN TO GOOD 0028 00027000
*                                      RETURN CODE                   */ 00028000
         SR    @03,@03                                             0028 00029000
         ST    @03,SSOBRETN(,SSOBPTR)                              0028 00030000
*   IF SSOBFUNC=SSOBTERM THEN                                      0029 00031000
         CLC   SSOBFUNC(2,SSOBPTR),@CH00038                        0029 00032000
         BNE   @RF00029                                            0029 00033000
*     DO;                           /* IF THE FUNCTION CODE IS FOR 0030 00034000
*                                      JOB TERMINATION PROCESS THE 0030 00035000
*                                      REQUEST.                      */ 00036000
*       IF SSIBJBID(5:8)=BLANKS THEN/* IF THE LAST FOUR CHARACTERS OF   00037000
*                                      THE JOB ID ARE BLANK THEN   0031 00038000
*                                      PROCEED. IF THE LAST FOUR   0031 00039000
*                                      CHARACTERS ARE NOT BLANKS THE    00040000
*                                      NAME IN THE JOBID FIELD CANNOT   00041000
*                                      BE THE NAME OF A SUBSYSTEM.   */ 00042000
         L     @03,SSOBSSIB(,SSOBPTR)                              0031 00043000
         CLC   SSIBJBID+4(4,@03),BLANKS                            0031 00044000
         BNE   @RF00031                                            0031 00045000
*         DO WHILE SSCVTPTR¬=0;     /* SCAN THE SSCVT CHAIN UNTIL A     00046000
*                                      MATCHING SUBSYSTEM NAME HAS 0032 00047000
*                                      BEEN FOUND OR UNTIL THE END OF   00048000
*                                      THE SSCVT CHAIN HAS BEEN    0032 00049000
*                                      REACHED                       */ 00050000
         B     @DE00032                                            0032 00051000
@DL00032 DS    0H                                                  0033 00052000
*           IF SSIBJBID(1:4)=SSCTSNAM THEN                         0033 00053000
         L     @03,SSOBSSIB(,SSOBPTR)                              0033 00054000
         CLC   SSIBJBID(4,@03),SSCTSNAM(SSCVTPTR)                  0033 00055000
         BNE   @RF00033                                            0033 00056000
*             RETURN CODE(0);       /* IF THE JOBNAME IN THE JOBID 0034 00057000
*                                      FIELD OF THE SSIB IS THE NAME    00058000
*                                      OF A SUBSYSTEM, THEN RETURN TO   00059000
*                                      CALLER WITH SSOBRETN AND    0034 00060000
*                                      REGISTER 15 = ZERO            */ 00061000
         SR    @15,@15                                             0034 00062000
         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0034 00063000
         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0034 00064000
         BR    @14                                                 0034 00065000
*           SSCVTPTR=SSCTSCTA;      /* GET PTR TO NEXT SSCVT         */ 00066000
@RF00033 L     @03,SSCTSCTA(,SSCVTPTR)                             0035 00067000
         LR    SSCVTPTR,@03                                        0035 00068000
*         END;                                                     0036 00069000
@DE00032 LTR   SSCVTPTR,SSCVTPTR                                   0036 00070000
         BNZ   @DL00032                                            0036 00071000
*     END;                                                         0037 00072000
@RF00031 DS    0H                                                  0038 00073000
*   SSOBRETN=SSJTPERR;              /* SET ERROR RETURN CODE IN    0038 00074000
*                                      SSOBRETN                      */ 00075000
@RF00029 MVC   SSOBRETN(4,SSOBPTR),@CF00765                        0038 00076000
*   RETURN CODE(0);                 /* RETURN TO CALLER              */ 00077000
         SR    @15,@15                                             0039 00078000
         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0039 00079000
         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0039 00080000
         BR    @14                                                 0039 00081000

         END   IEFJJTRM                                                 00864000
./  ADD  SSI=33170858,NAME=IEFJRASP
         TITLE 'IEFJRASP-ROUTE TO ALL ACTIVE SUBSYSTEMS                *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IEFJRASP CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IEFJRASP  73.317'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00014000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00015000
         LR    @11,@01                                             0001 00016000
         USING @DATD,@11                                           0001 00017000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00018000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00019000
         ST    @11,8(,@13)                                         0001 00020000
         LR    @13,@11                                             0001 00021000
*   SSOBPTR=SSOBADDR;               /* SET UP ADDRESSABILITY FOR THE    00022000
*                                      SSOB                          */ 00023000
         ST    SSOBADDR,SSOBPTR                                    0038 00024000
*   SSCVTPTR=JESSSCT;               /* GET THE ADDR OF THE FIRST   0039 00025000
*                                      SSCVT                         */ 00026000
         L     @10,CVTPTR                                          0039 00027000
         L     @10,CVTJESCT(,@10)                                  0039 00028000
         L     SSCVTPTR,JESSSCT(,@10)                              0039 00029000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0040 00030000
*    (SSCVTADR,                                                    0040 00031000
*     SSOBADDR) UNRSTD;                                            0040 00032000
*   SSIBSAVE=SSOBSSIB;              /* SAVE PTR TO CALLER'S SSIB     */ 00033000
         L     @10,SSOBPTR                                         0041 00034000
         L     SSIBSAVE,SSOBSSIB(,@10)                             0041 00035000
*   R15RTNCD=INITRTN;               /* INITIALIZE THE RETURN CODE  0042 00036000
*                                      FROM THE SUBSYSTEM INTERFACE     00037000
*                                      TO '7FFFFFFF'X                */ 00038000
         L     R15RTNCD,INITRTN                                    0042 00039000
*   SSRTNCD=INITRTN1;               /* INITIALIZE THE RETURN CODE  0043 00040000
*                                      FROM THE SUBSYSTEMS TO ZERO   */ 00041000
         L     @15,INITRTN1                                        0043 00042000
         LR    SSRTNCD,@15                                         0043 00043000
*   SSOBRETN=INITRTN1;              /* INITIALIZE THE RETURN CODE IN    00044000
*                                      THE SSOB TO ZERO      @YM01982*/ 00045000
*                                                                  0044 00046000
         ST    @15,SSOBRETN(,@10)                                  0044 00047000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00048000
*   /*                                                               */ 00049000
*   /* THE FOLLOWING CODE GET CORE FOR A SSIB AND COPY THE INPUT SSIB*/ 00050000
*   /* INTO IT,SCANS THE SSCVT CHAIN,PUTS THE NAME OF THE SUBSYSTEM  */ 00051000
*   /* ASSOCIATED WITH EACH SSCVT IN THE SSIB, AND ISSUES THE        */ 00052000
*   /* IEFSSREQ MACRO. THIS IS DONE FOR EACH SUBSYSTEM EXCEPT THE    */ 00053000
*   /* MASTER. ON RETURN FROM THE IEFSSREQ CALL, THE RETURN CODES    */ 00054000
*   /* FROM THE SUBSYSTEM INTERFACE AND THE SUBSYSTEM ARE COMPARED   */ 00055000
*   /* WITH THE EXISTING RETURN CODES. IF THE RETURN CODE FROM THE   */ 00056000
*   /* SUBSYSTEM INTERFACE IS LESS THAN OR EQUAL TO THE CURRENT      */ 00057000
*   /* LOWEST THEN REPLACE THE CURRENT LOWEST INTERFACE RETURN CODE  */ 00058000
*   /* AND SAVE THE LARGER OF THE TWO RETURN CODES FROM THE          */ 00059000
*   /* SUBSYSTEM. AFTER ALL SUBSYSTEMS HAVE BEEN INVOKED, CONTROL IS */ 00060000
*   /* RETURNED TO THE CALLER PASSING BACK THE RETURN CODES.         */ 00061000
*   /*                                                               */ 00062000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00063000
*                                                                  0045 00064000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0045 00065000
*    (R0,                                                          0045 00066000
*     R1) RSTD;                                                    0045 00067000
*   R0=LENGTH(SSIB);                /* GET LENGTH OF SSIB            */ 00068000
         LA    R0,36                                               0046 00069000
*   R0=R0|SUBPOOL;                  /* PUT IN SUBPOOL #              */ 00070000
         O     R0,SUBPOOL                                          0047 00071000
*   GEN(GETMAIN R,LV=(0));          /* GET CORE FOR ROUTE TO ALL SSIB*/ 00072000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(0)                                               00073000
*   SSIBRTE(1:SSIBLEN)=SSIB;        /* COPY INPUT SSIB TO ROUTE TO 0049 00074000
*                                      ALL SSIB                      */ 00075000
         L     @10,SSOBPTR                                         0049 00076000
         L     @15,SSOBSSIB(,@10)                                  0049 00077000
         LH    @14,SSIBLEN(,@15)                                   0049 00078000
         BCTR  @14,0                                               0049 00079000
         EX    @14,@SM00729                                        0049 00080000
*   SSOBSSIB=R1;                    /* CHAIN THE NEW SSIB TO THE SSOB*/ 00081000
         ST    R1,SSOBSSIB(,@10)                                   0050 00082000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0051 00083000
*    (R0,                                                          0051 00084000
*     R1) UNRSTD;                                                  0051 00085000
*   DO WHILE SSCVTPTR¬=0;           /* INVOKE EACH SUBSYSTEM       0052 00086000
*                                      ASSOCIATED WITH AN SSCVT    0052 00087000
*                                      EXCEPT THE MASTER             */ 00088000
         B     @DE00052                                            0052 00089000
@DL00052 DS    0H                                                  0053 00090000
*     IF SSCTSNAM¬=MSTR THEN                                       0053 00091000
         CLC   SSCTSNAM(4,SSCVTPTR),MSTR                           0053 00092000
         BE    @RF00053                                            0053 00093000
*       DO;                         /* PROCESS FOR EACH SUBSYSTEM  0054 00094000
*                                      EXCEPT THE MASTER             */ 00095000
*         ENDLIST='1'B;             /* SET END OF LIST INDICATOR IN     00096000
*                                      THE IEFSSREQ PARAMETER LIST   */ 00097000
         OI    ENDLIST,B'10000000'                                 0055 00098000
*         SSIBSSNM=SSCTSNAM;        /* PUT THE SUBSYSTEM NAME IN THE    00099000
*                                      SSIB                          */ 00100000
         L     @10,SSOBPTR                                         0056 00101000
         L     @10,SSOBSSIB(,@10)                                  0056 00102000
         MVC   SSIBSSNM(4,@10),SSCTSNAM(SSCVTPTR)                  0056 00103000
*         RESPECIFY                                                0057 00104000
*           PARMPTR RSTD;                                          0057 00105000
*         PARMPTR=ADDR(PARMLIST);   /* PUT PARMLIST LIST ADDR IN REG    00106000
*                                      1                           0058 00107000
*                                                                    */ 00108000
         LA    PARMPTR,PARMLIST                                    0058 00109000
*                                                                  0059 00110000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00111000
*         /*                                                         */ 00112000
*         /* ? IEFSSREQ;                                             */ 00113000
*         /*                                                         */ 00114000
*         /***********************************************************/ 00115000
*                                                                  0059 00116000
*/*                                                                  */ 00117000
*/*  PASS CONTROL TO JOB ENTRY SUBSYSTEM TO                          */ 00118000
*/*  PROCESS REQUEST -                                               */ 00119000
*/*                                                                  */ 00120000
*/*    INPUT - REGISTER 1 POINTS TO A ONE-                           */ 00121000
*/*            WORD PARAMETER LIST WHICH                             */ 00122000
*/*            POINTS TO THE SSOB                                    */ 00123000
*/*                                                                  */ 00124000
*                                                                  0059 00125000
*         CALL SSREQ;                                              0059 00126000
         L     @10,CVTPTR                                          0059 00127000
         L     @10,CVTJESCT(,@10)                                  0059 00128000
         L     @15,JESSSREQ(,@10)                                  0059 00129000
         BALR  @14,@15                                             0059 00130000
*         RESPECIFY                                                0060 00131000
*           PARMPTR UNRSTD;                                        0060 00132000
*         RESPECIFY                                                0061 00133000
*           RTNCODE RSTD;                                          0061 00134000
*         IF RTNCODE¬>R15RTNCD THEN                                0062 00135000
         CR    RTNCODE,R15RTNCD                                    0062 00136000
         BH    @RF00062                                            0062 00137000
*           DO;                     /* IF THE RETURN CODE FROM THE 0063 00138000
*                                      SUBSYSTEM INTERFACE IS NOT  0063 00139000
*                                      LARGER THAN THE CURRENT     0063 00140000
*                                      LARGEST,THEN REPLACE THE    0063 00141000
*                                      CURRENT SMALLEST WITH THE NEW    00142000
*                                      SMALLEST                      */ 00143000
*             IF RTNCODE<R15RTNCD THEN                             0064 00144000
         CR    RTNCODE,R15RTNCD                                    0064 00145000
         BNL   @RF00064                                            0064 00146000
*               DO;                 /* IF THE R15 RETURN CODE IS   0065 00147000
*                                      SMALLER, REPLACE R15 AND    0065 00148000
*                                      SSOBRETN CODES                */ 00149000
*                 R15RTNCD=RTNCODE; /* REPLACE R15 RETURN CODE       */ 00150000
         LR    R15RTNCD,RTNCODE                                    0066 00151000
*                 SSRTNCD=SSOBRETN; /* REPLACE SSOB RETURN CODE      */ 00152000
         L     @14,SSOBPTR                                         0067 00153000
         L     SSRTNCD,SSOBRETN(,@14)                              0067 00154000
*               END;                                               0068 00155000
*                                                                  0068 00156000
*/*   NOTE- IF THE RETURN CODES ARE EQUAL, WE STILL WANT TO        0069 00157000
*     EXECUTE THE CODE BECAUSE OF THE POSSIBILITY OF THE RETURN    0069 00158000
*     CODE FROM THE SUBSYSTEM BEING LARGER THAN THE CURRENT.         */ 00159000
*                                                                  0069 00160000
*             ELSE                                                 0069 00161000
*               IF SSOBRETN>SSRTNCD THEN                           0069 00162000
         B     @RC00064                                            0069 00163000
@RF00064 L     @14,SSOBPTR                                         0069 00164000
         L     @14,SSOBRETN(,@14)                                  0069 00165000
         CR    @14,SSRTNCD                                         0069 00166000
         BNH   @RF00069                                            0069 00167000
*                 SSRTNCD=SSOBRETN; /* IF THE SUBSYSTEM JUST INVOKED    00168000
*                                      RETURNED A LARGER RETURN CODE    00169000
*                                      THAN THE CURRENT LARGEST,THEN    00170000
*                                      REPLACE THE CURRENT LARGEST 0070 00171000
*                                      WITH THE NEW LARGEST          */ 00172000
         LR    SSRTNCD,@14                                         0070 00173000
*           END;                                                   0071 00174000
@RF00069 DS    0H                                                  0071 00175000
@RC00064 DS    0H                                                  0072 00176000
*         RESPECIFY                                                0072 00177000
*           RTNCODE UNRSTD;                                        0072 00178000
@RF00062 DS    0H                                                  0073 00179000
*       END;                                                       0073 00180000
*     SSCVTPTR=SSCTSCTA;            /* GET PTR TO NEXT SSCVT         */ 00181000
@RF00053 L     SSCVTPTR,SSCTSCTA(,SSCVTPTR)                        0074 00182000
*   END;                                                           0075 00183000
@DE00052 LTR   SSCVTPTR,SSCVTPTR                                   0075 00184000
         BNZ   @DL00052                                            0075 00185000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0076 00186000
*    (R0,                                                          0076 00187000
*     R1) RSTD;                                                    0076 00188000
*   R0=LENGTH(SSIB);                                               0077 00189000
         LA    R0,36                                               0077 00190000
*   R0=R0|SUBPOOL;                  /* PUT SUBPOOL # WITH SSIB LENGTH*/ 00191000
         O     R0,SUBPOOL                                          0078 00192000
*   R1=SSOBSSIB;                    /* PUT ADDR OF SSIB IN REG 1     */ 00193000
         L     @10,SSOBPTR                                         0079 00194000
         L     R1,SSOBSSIB(,@10)                                   0079 00195000
*   GEN(FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1));   /* FREE THE ROUTE TO ALL SSIB    */ 00196000
         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00197000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0081 00198000
*    (R0,                                                          0081 00199000
*     R1) UNRSTD;                                                  0081 00200000
*   SSOBSSIB=SSIBSAVE;              /* RESTORE THE ISSUER'S SUBSYSTEM   00201000
*                                      NAME                          */ 00202000
         L     @10,SSOBPTR                                         0082 00203000
         ST    SSIBSAVE,SSOBSSIB(,@10)                             0082 00204000
*   SSOBRETN=SSRTNCD;               /* RETURN THE LARGEST RETURN CODE   00205000
*                                      PASSED BACK FROM A SUBSYSTEM  */ 00206000
         ST    SSRTNCD,SSOBRETN(,@10)                              0083 00207000
*   RETURN CODE(R15RTNCD);          /* RETURN THE LARGEST RETURN CODE   00208000
*                                      FROM THE SUBSYSTEM INTERFACE     00209000
*                                      TO THE CALLER                 */ 00210000
         L     @13,4(,@13)                                         0084 00211000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0084 00212000
         LR    @01,@11                                             0084 00213000
         FREEMAIN R,LV=(0),A=(1)                                        00214000
         LR    @15,@03                                             0084 00215000
         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0084 00216000
         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0084 00217000
         BR    @14                                                 0084 00218000
*   END IEFJRASP                                                   0085 00219000
*                                                                  0085 00220000
*/* THE FOLLOWING INCLUDE STATEMENTS WERE FOUND IN THIS PROGRAM.     */ 00221000
