@ENDDATA EQU   *                                                        00930000
         END   IEFJRASP                                                 00931000
./  ADD  SSI=23410040,NAME=IEFJREAD
         TITLE 'IEFJREAD - PSEUDO ACCESS METHOD READ A SEQUENTIAL REC'  00001000
IEFJREAD CSECT ,                                                   0001 00002000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00003000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00004000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00005000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00006000
         DC    C'IEFJREAD  72.341'                                 0001 00007000
         DROP  @15                                                      00008000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00009000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00010000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00011000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00012000
*   RPLPTR=R1;                      /* SAVE THE POINTER TO THE RPL   */ 00013000
         LR    RPLPTR,R1                                           0008 00014000
*   RFY                                                            0009 00015000
*     R1 UNRSTD;                                                   0009 00016000
*   RFY                                                            0010 00017000
*     IFGRPL BASED(RPLPTR);         /* THE RPL MACRO IS BASED ON   0010 00018000
*                                      RPLPTR                        */ 00019000
*   RFY                                                            0011 00020000
*     IFGACB BASED(RPLDACB);        /* THE ACB IS BASED ON A PTR IN     00021000
*                                      THE RPL                       */ 00022000
*   RFY                                                            0012 00023000
*     ACBPRFIX BASED(ADDR(IFGACB)-4);/* GET THE ACB PREFIX           */ 00024000
*   RFY                                                            0013 00025000
*     IEFJAMWD BASED(ACBPRFIX);     /* THE ACCESS METHOD WORK AREA IS   00026000
*                                      BASED ON THE ACB PREFIX       */ 00027000
*   RFY                                                            0014 00028000
*     IEFJAREA BASED(CURNTREC);     /* THE COMMON DATA RECORD AREA IS   00029000
*                                      BASED ON A PTR TO THE REC TO     00030000
*                                      BE READ                       */ 00031000
*                                                                  0015 00032000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00033000
*   /*                                                               */ 00034000
*   /* PERFORM A SEQUENTIAL READ                                     */ 00035000
*   /*                                                               */ 00036000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00037000
*                                                                  0015 00038000
*   CURNTREC=AMWDLAST;              /* SET PTR OF REC TO BE READ     */ 00039000
         L     @10,RPLDACB(,RPLPTR)                                0015 00040000
         AL    @10,@CF00232                                        0015 00041000
         L     @10,ACBPRFIX(,@10)                                  0015 00042000
         L     CURNTREC,AMWDLAST(,@10)                             0015 00043000
*   AMWDLAST=NEXTPTR;               /* THE LAST REC NEXTPTR IS IS  0016 00044000
*                                      USED TO GET THE NEW REC. THE     00045000
*                                      REC FORMAT IS BASED ON      0016 00046000
*                                      AMWDLAST                      */ 00047000
         L     @05,NEXTPTR(,CURNTREC)                              0016 00048000
         ST    @05,AMWDLAST(,@10)                                  0016 00049000
*   IF NEXTPTR=0 THEN               /* DO A LOOK AHEAD AT THE NEW  0017 00050000
*                                      NEXTPTR                       */ 00051000
         LTR   @05,@05                                             0017 00052000
         BNZ   @RF00017                                            0017 00053000
*     AMWDEOF=ON;                   /* IF EQUAL TO ZERO THIS IS THE     00054000
*                                      LAST REC SO TURN ON EOF BIT   */ 00055000
         OI    AMWDEOF(@10),B'10000000'                            0018 00056000
*   TEXTPTR=RPLAREA;                /* TEXTPTR POINTS TO THE WHERE 0019 00057000
*                                      THE REC WILL BE READ INTO     */ 00058000
@RF00017 L     TEXTPTR,RPLAREA(,RPLPTR)                            0019 00059000
*   RECPTR=ADDR(IEFJAREA);          /* POINT TO THE REC TO BE READ   */ 00060000
         LR    RECPTR,CURNTREC                                     0020 00061000
*   IF AMWDMV80=ON THEN             /* IS THE REC TO BE READ A FIXED    00062000
*                                      LENGTH                        */ 00063000
         L     @10,RPLDACB(,RPLPTR)                                0021 00064000
         AL    @10,@CF00232                                        0021 00065000
         L     @10,ACBPRFIX(,@10)                                  0021 00066000
         TM    AMWDMV80(@10),B'01000000'                           0021 00067000
         BNO   @RF00021                                            0021 00068000
*     TEXTAREA(1:80)=RECTEXT(1:80); /* MOVE A FIXED LGTH REC         */ 00069000
         MVC   TEXTAREA(80,TEXTPTR),RECTEXT(CURNTREC)              0022 00070000
*   ELSE                            /* IF THE AMWDMV80 BIT IS OFF  0023 00071000
*                                      MOVE THE VARIABLE LENGTH    0023 00072000
*                                      RECTEXT TO THE SPECIFIED AREA */ 00073000
*     DO;                                                          0023 00074000
         B     @RC00021                                            0023 00075000
@RF00021 DS    0H                                                  0024 00076000
*       TEXTLGTH=LGTH-8;            /* GET THE ACTUAL LGTH           */ 00077000
         L     TEXTLGTH,LGTH(,CURNTREC)                            0024 00078000
         SH    TEXTLGTH,@CH00050                                   0024 00079000
*       IF TEXTLGTH<=256 THEN       /* IF GREATER THEN 256 MORE THEN    00080000
*                                      ONE MOVE IS NECESSARY         */ 00081000
         CH    TEXTLGTH,@CH00231                                   0025 00082000
         BH    @RF00025                                            0025 00083000
*         TEXTAREA(1:TEXTLGTH)=RECTEXT(1:TEXTLGTH);/* MOVE ONCE AND     00084000
*                                      END                           */ 00085000
         LR    @10,TEXTLGTH                                        0026 00086000
         BCTR  @10,0                                               0026 00087000
         EX    @10,@SM00234                                        0026 00088000
*       ELSE                                                       0027 00089000
*         DO;                       /* MORE THEN ONE MOVE IS       0027 00090000

*                                                                  0035 00023000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00024000
*   /*                                                               */ 00025000

*   DO;                             /* GETMAIN (R) LV(SUBLEN)SP(230) */ 00074000

*                 DO;               /* GETMAIN (R) LV(SUBLEN)SP(230) */ 00202000

./  ADD  SSI=63290412,NAME=IEFJSDTN
         TITLE 'IEFJSDTN-SUBSYSTEM DETERMINATION                       *00001000

IEFJSDTN CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IEFJSDTN  76.329'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
*   IF SSOBINDV¬=ZERO&              /* WAS AN SSOBVS PASSED? @G29AN2F*/ 00014000
*       SSVSLEN¬=LENGTH(SSVS) THEN  /* AND IS THE LENGTH INVALID   0032 00015000
*                                                            @G29AN2F*/ 00016000
         L     @03,SSOBINDV(,SSOBPTR)                              0032 00017000
         LTR   @03,@03                                             0032 00018000
         BZ    @RF00032                                            0032 00019000
         CLC   SSVSLEN(2,@03),@CH00066                             0032 00020000
         BE    @RF00032                                            0032 00021000
*     RETURN CODE(SSRTLERR);        /* YES, RETURN WITH LOGIC ERROR     00022000
*                                      RETURN CODE           @G29AN2F*/ 00023000
         LA    @15,20                                              0033 00024000
         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0033 00025000
         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0033 00026000
         BR    @14                                                 0033 00027000
*   SSCVTPTR=JESSSCT;               /* GET ADDR OF FIRST SSCVT       */ 00028000
@RF00032 L     @15,CVTPTR                                          0034 00029000
         L     @15,CVTJESCT(,@15)                                  0034 00030000
         L     SSCVTPTR,JESSSCT(,@15)                              0034 00031000
*   IF SSIBJBID(5:8)=BLANKS THEN    /* IF THE LAST 4 CHARACTERS IN 0035 00032000
*                                      THE JOBID FIELD ARE NOT BLANK,   00033000
*                                      THE NAME CANNOT BE THE NAME OF   00034000
*                                      A SUBSYSTEM           @G29AN2F*/ 00035000
         L     @03,SSOBSSIB(,SSOBPTR)                              0035 00036000
         CLC   SSIBJBID+4(4,@03),BLANKS                            0035 00037000
         BNE   @RF00035                                            0035 00038000
*     DO WHILE SSCVTPTR¬=0;         /* SCAN THE SSCVT CHAIN UNTIL A     00039000
*                                      MATCHING SUBSYSTEM NAME HAS 0036 00040000
*                                      BEEN FOUND OR UNTIL THE END OF   00041000
*                                      THE SSCVT CHAIN HAS BEEN    0036 00042000
*                                      REACHED                       */ 00043000

@DL00036 DS    0H                                                  0037 00045000
*       IF SSIBJBID(1:4)=SSCTSNAM THEN                             0037 00046000

*         DO;                       /* IF THE JOBNAME IN THE JOBID 0038 00050000
*                                      FIELD OF THE SSIB IS THE NAME    00051000
*                                      OF A SUBSYSTEM, THEN PROCESS     00052000
*                                      THE SSCVT.            @G29AN2F*/ 00053000
*           IF SSOBINDV¬=ZERO THEN                                 0039 00054000
         L     @03,SSOBINDV(,SSOBPTR)                              0039 00055000
         LTR   @03,@03                                             0039 00056000
         BZ    @RF00039                                            0039 00057000
*             SSVSSCTP=SSCVTPTR;    /* IF AN SSOBVS EXTENSION WAS  0040 00058000
*                                      PASSED, PUT THE POINTER TO THE   00059000
*                                      SSCVT IN THE EXTENSION.     0040 00060000
*                                                            @G29AN2F*/ 00061000
         ST    SSCVTPTR,SSVSSCTP(,@03)                             0040 00062000
*           IF SSIBJBID(1:4)=JESPJESN THEN                         0041 00063000
@RF00039 L     @03,SSOBSSIB(,SSOBPTR)                              0041 00064000

         L     @15,CVTJESCT(,@15)                                  0041 00066000
         CLC   SSIBJBID(4,@03),JESPJESN(@15)                       0041 00067000
         BNE   @RF00041                                            0041 00068000
*             SSIBPJES='1'B;        /* IF THIS IS THE NAME OF THE  0042 00069000
*                                      PRIMARY SUBSYSTEM, SET THE  0042 00070000
*                                      PRIMARY SUBSYSTEM INDICATOR IN   00071000
*                                      THE SSIB.                     */ 00072000
         OI    SSIBPJES(@03),B'10000000'                           0042 00073000
*           ELSE                    /* OTHERWISE CHECK IF THE      0043 00074000
*                                      SUBSYSTEM MUST BE STARTED WITH   00075000

*                                      SUBSYSTEM SERVICES    @G29AN2F*/ 00077000
*             IF SSOBINDV¬=ZERO THEN/* WAS AN EXTENSION PASSED?    0043 00078000
*                                                            @G29AN2F*/ 00079000

*               IF SSCTUPSS='1'B THEN                              0044 00084000
         TM    SSCTUPSS(SSCVTPTR),B'01000000'                      0044 00085000

*                 DO;               /* YES, THEN IF SUBSYSTEM IS TO     00087000
*                                      BE STARTED WITH THE PRIMARY 0045 00088000

*                   SSVSUPSS='1'B;  /* SET INDICATOR         @G29AN2F*/ 00090000

*                   SSIBSSNM=JESPJESN;/* PUT THE PRIMARY SUBSYSTEM 0047 00092000
*                                      NAME IN THE SUBSYSTEM NAME  0047 00093000
*                                      FIELD OF THE SSIB.    @G29AN2F*/ 00094000

         L     @15,CVTPTR                                          0047 00096000
         L     @15,CVTJESCT(,@15)                                  0047 00097000
         MVC   SSIBSSNM(4,@03),JESPJESN(@15)                       0047 00098000
*                 END;              /*                       @G29AN2F*/ 00099000
*               ELSE                                               0049 00100000
*                 SSVSUPSS='0'B;    /* SET NORMAL START INDICATOR  0049 00101000
*                                                            @G29AN2F*/ 00102000
         B     @RC00044                                            0049 00103000
@RF00044 L     @03,SSOBINDV(,SSOBPTR)                              0049 00104000
         NI    SSVSUPSS(@03),B'01111111'                           0049 00105000
*           SSOBRETN=SSVSSNAM;      /* INDICATE THE JOBID FIELD IN 0050 00106000
*                                      THE SSIB CONTAINS THE NAME OF    00107000
*                                      A SUBSYSTEM.                  */ 00108000
@RC00044 DS    0H                                                  0050 00109000
@RF00043 DS    0H                                                  0050 00110000
@RC00041 SLR   @03,@03                                             0050 00111000

*           RETURN CODE(SSRTOK);    /* INDICATE NO ERROR FOUND       */ 00113000

         L     @14,12(,@13)                                        0051 00115000
         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0051 00116000
         BR    @14                                                 0051 00117000
*         END;                                                     0052 00118000
*       SSCVTPTR=SSCTSCTA;          /* GET PTR TO NEXT SSCVT         */ 00119000
@RF00037 L     SSCVTPTR,SSCTSCTA(,SSCVTPTR)                        0053 00120000
*     END;                                                         0054 00121000
@DE00036 LTR   SSCVTPTR,SSCVTPTR                                   0054 00122000

*   SSIBSSNM=JESPJESN;              /* PUT THE PRIMARY SUBSYSTEM NAME   00124000

*                                      THE SSIB.                     */ 00126000
@RF00035 L     @03,SSOBSSIB(,SSOBPTR)                              0055 00127000

*   SSOBRETN=SSVSJBNM;              /* INDICATE THE NAME IN THE JOBID   00131000

*   RETURN CODE(SSRTOK);            /* INDICATE NO ERROR FOUND       */ 00135000

         LM    @00,@12,20(@13)                                     0057 00138000
         BR    @14                                                 0057 00139000

./  ADD  SSI=63290413,NAME=IEFJSINT
         TITLE 'SUBSYSTEM INTERFACE INITIALIZATION ROUTINE - IEFJSINT  *00001000
                        '                                               00002000
IEFJSINT CSECT ,                                                   0001 00003000
@MAINENT DS    0H                                                  0001 00004000
         USING *,@15                                               0001 00005000
         B     @PROLOG                                             0001 00006000
         DC    AL1(16)                                             0001 00007000
         DC    C'IEFJSINT  76.329'                                 0001 00008000
         DROP  @15                                                      00009000
@PROLOG  STM   @14,@12,12(@13)                                     0001 00010000
         BALR  @12,0                                               0001 00011000
@PSTART  DS    0H                                                  0001 00012000
         USING @PSTART,@12                                         0001 00013000
         L     @00,@SIZDATD                                        0001 00014000
         GETMAIN  R,LV=(0)                                              00015000
         LR    @11,@01                                             0001 00016000
         USING @DATD,@11                                           0001 00017000
         ST    @13,@SA00001+4                                      0001 00018000
         LM    @00,@01,20(@13)                                     0001 00019000
         ST    @11,8(,@13)                                         0001 00020000
         LR    @13,@11                                             0001 00021000
*                                                                  0103 00022000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00023000
*   /*                                                               */ 00024000
*   /* START OF IEFJSINT PROCESSING                          @G29ANSS*/ 00025000
*   /*                                                               */ 00026000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00027000
*                                                                  0103 00028000
*   JESTBPTR=ADDR(IEFJTBNM);        /* SET JES NAMES TABLE PTR       */ 00029000
         L     JESTBPTR,@CV00079                                   0103 00030000
*   JESPJESN=TBLENTRY;              /* SET PRIMARY JOB ENTRY       0104 00031000
*                                      SUBSYSTEM NAME IN JESCT       */ 00032000
*                                                                  0104 00033000
         L     @10,CVTPTR                                          0104 00034000
         L     @10,CVTJESCT(,@10)                                  0104 00035000
         MVC   JESPJESN(4,@10),TBLENTRY(JESTBPTR)                  0104 00036000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00037000
*   /*                                                               */ 00038000
*   /* LOAD ADDRESS OF SUBSYSTEM REQUEST ROUTINE - IEFJSREQ          */ 00039000
*   /*                                                               */ 00040000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00041000
*                                                                  0105 00042000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0105 00043000
*    (R0PTR) RESTRICTED;                                           0105 00044000
*   GEN(LOAD  EP=IEFJSREQ);                                        0106 00045000
         LOAD  EP=IEFJSREQ                                              00046000
*   GEN(SPACE);                                                    0107 00047000
         SPACE                                                          00048000
*   JESSSREQ=R0PTR;                 /* SET ADDRESS IN JESCT          */ 00049000
         L     @10,CVTPTR                                          0108 00050000
         L     @01,CVTJESCT(,@10)                                  0108 00051000
         ST    R0PTR,JESSSREQ(,@01)                                0108 00052000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0109 00053000
*    (R0PTR) UNRESTRICTED;                                         0109 00054000
*   GEN(DELETE EP=IEFJSREQ);                                       0110 00055000
         DELETE EP=IEFJSREQ                                             00056000
         EJECT                                                          00057000
*                                                                  0111 00058000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00059000
*   /*                                                               */ 00060000
*   /* THE FOLLOWING LOOP WILL GO THROUGH THE ENTRIES IN THE JES     */ 00061000
*   /* NAMES TABLE. FOR EACH ENTRY SCANSSCT IS CALLED WHICH CHECKS TO*/ 00062000
*   /* SEE IF THE ENTRY IS A DUPLICATE OF A SUBSYSTEM NAME. IF IT IS */ 00063000
*   /* THEN SKIP IT OTHERWISE BLDSSCVT IS CALLED WHICH BUILDS A SSCVT*/ 00064000
*   /* FOR THE SUBSYSTEM NAME, CHAINS THE SSCVT OFF THE JESCT AND    */ 00065000
*   /* KEEPS A COUNT OF THE NUMBER OF DEFINED SUBSYSTEMS. WHEN THE   */ 00066000
*   /* SSCVT IS BUILT FOR THE MASTER SUBSYSTEM THEN BLDSSCVT CALLS   */ 00067000
*   /* BLDMSSVT TO BUILD THE MASTER SUBSYSTEM VECTOR TABLE.  @G29ANSS*/ 00068000
*   /*                                                               */ 00069000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00070000
*                                                                  0111 00071000
*   NUMSUBS=ZERO;                   /* INITIALIZE COUNT OF DEFINED 0111 00072000
*                                      SUBSYSTEMS            @G29AN2F*/ 00073000
         SLR   NUMSUBS,NUMSUBS                                     0111 00074000
*   DO WHILE(TBLENTRY¬='00000000'X);                               0112 00075000
         B     @DE00112                                            0112 00076000
@DL00112 DS    0H                                                  0113 00077000
*     CALL SCANSSCT(TBLENTRY);      /* SCAN SSCVT CHAIN SEARCHING FOR   00078000
*                                      A DUPLICATE SUBSYSTEM NAME. 0113 00079000
*                                      DUPSW IS SET ON OR OFF BY   0113 00080000
*                                      SCANSSCT              @G29ANSS*/ 00081000
         ST    JESTBPTR,@AL00001                                   0113 00082000
         LA    @01,@AL00001                                        0113 00083000
         BAL   @14,SCANSSCT                                        0113 00084000
*     IF DUPSW=OFF THEN             /* ANY DUPLICATES FOUND? @G29ANSS*/ 00085000
         TM    DUPSW,B'10000000'                                   0114 00086000
         BNZ   @RF00114                                            0114 00087000
*       CALL BLDSSCVT(TBLENTRY);    /* NO, BUILD THE SSCVT FOR THE 0115 00088000
*                                      SUBSYSTEM. PASS THE NAME OF 0115 00089000
*                                      THE SUBSYSTEM TO BE BUILT.  0115 00090000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00091000
         ST    JESTBPTR,@AL00001                                   0115 00092000
         LA    @01,@AL00001                                        0115 00093000
         BAL   @14,BLDSSCVT                                        0115 00094000
*     JESTBPTR=JESTBPTR+NTRYSIZ;    /* UPDATE JES NAMES TABLE ENTRY     00095000
*                                      POINTER                       */ 00096000
@RF00114 AL    JESTBPTR,@CF00063                                   0116 00097000
*   END;                                                           0117 00098000
@DE00112 CLC   TBLENTRY(4,JESTBPTR),@CB01082                       0117 00099000
         BNE   @DL00112                                            0117 00100000
         EJECT                                                          00101000
*                                                                  0118 00102000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00103000
*   /*                                                               */ 00104000
*   /* CHECK TO SEE IF THIS IS AN SU29 SYSTEM. IF SO THEN FIND THE   */ 00105000
*   /* MODULE IEFJSSNT(CONTAINS THE NAMES AND INITIALIZATION ENTRY   */ 00106000
*   /* POINTS OF SUBSYSTEMS). LINK TO EACH SUBSYSTEM INITIALIZATION  */ 00107000
*   /* ROUTINES.                                             @G29ANSS*/ 00108000
*   /*                                                               */ 00109000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00110000
*                                                                  0118 00111000
*   IF SU29BIT=ON THEN              /* IS THIS AN SU29 SYSTEM?     0118 00112000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00113000
         L     @10,CVTPTR                                          0118 00114000
         L     @10,CVTIHASU(,@10)                                  0118 00115000
         TM    SU29BIT(@10),B'00000100'                            0118 00116000
         BNO   @RF00118                                            0118 00117000
*     DO;                           /* YES, FIND IEFJSSNT    @G29ANSS*/ 00118000
*                                                                  0119 00119000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00120000
*       /*                                                           */ 00121000
*       /* FIND MODULE IEFJSSNT IN CONCATENATED SYS1.LINKLIB @G29ANSS*/ 00122000
*       /*                                                           */ 00123000
*       /*************************************************************/ 00124000
*                                                                  0120 00125000
*       BLDLNUM=ONE;                /* NUM ENTRIES IN BLDL LIST    0120 00126000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00127000
         MVC   BLDLNUM(2),@CH00047                                 0120 00128000
*       BLDLLEN=LENGTH(BLDLENTR);   /* LEN OF ENTRY          @G29ANSS*/ 00129000
         MVC   BLDLLEN(2),@CH00087                                 0121 00130000
*       BLDLNAME=JSSNT;             /* THE NAME TO LOCATE    @G29ANSS*/ 00131000
         MVC   BLDLNAME(8),@CC00102                                0122 00132000
*       BLDLDATA=BLDLDATA&&BLDLDATA;/* CLEAR FIELDS          @G29ANSS*/ 00133000
         XC    BLDLDATA(52),BLDLDATA                               0123 00134000
*       GEN REFS(BLDLLIST) SETS(BLDLDATA);                         0124 00135000
*                                            /* FIND JSSNT   @G29ANSS*/ 00136000
         BLDL  0,BLDLLIST         FIND MODULE IEFJSSNT         @G29ANSS 00137000
*       RFY                                                        0125 00138000
*         R15 RSTD;                 /*                       @G29ANSS*/ 00139000
*       IF R15=ZERO THEN            /* WAS IEFJSSNT FOUND?   @G29ANSS*/ 00140000
         LTR   R15,R15                                             0126 00141000
         BNZ   @RF00126                                            0126 00142000
*         DO;                       /* YES, LOAD IT          @G29ANSS*/ 00143000
*                                                                  0127 00144000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00145000
*           /*                                                       */ 00146000
*           /* LOAD MODULE IEFJSSNT                          @G29ANSS*/ 00147000
*           /*                                                       */ 00148000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00149000
*                                                                  0128 00150000
*           RFY                                                    0128 00151000
*             R0 RSTD;              /*                       @G29ANSS*/ 00152000
*           DO;                     /* LOAD DE(BLDLENTR)           0129 00153000
*                                      ERRET(LOADERR)                */ 00154000
*             RESPECIFY                                            0130 00155000
*              (GPR00P,                                            0130 00156000
*               GPR01P,                                            0130 00157000
*               GPR15F) RESTRICTED;                                0130 00158000
*             GPR00P=-ADDR(BLDLENTR);/* LOAD NEGATIVE OF LIST ENTRY     00159000
*                                      ADDR                          */ 00160000
         LA    GPR00P,BLDLENTR                                     0131 00161000
         LCR   GPR00P,GPR00P                                       0131 00162000
*             GPR01P=0;             /* JOBLIB OR LINKLIB DCB         */ 00163000
         SLR   GPR01P,GPR01P                                       0132 00164000
*             GPR01P=GPR01P|'80000000'X;/* ERROR RETURN LABEL      0133 00165000
*                                      SPECIFIED                     */ 00166000
         O     GPR01P,@CF01088                                     0133 00167000
*             SVC(8);               /* ISSUE LOAD SVC                */ 00168000
         SVC   8                                                   0134 00169000
*             IF GPR15F¬=0 THEN     /* LOAD WAS UNSUCCESSFUL         */ 00170000
         LTR   GPR15F,GPR15F                                       0135 00171000
         BNZ   @RT00135                                            0135 00172000
*               GOTO LOADERR;       /* BRANCH TO ERROR LOCATION      */ 00173000
*             RESPECIFY                                            0137 00174000
*              (GPR00P,                                            0137 00175000
*               GPR01P,                                            0137 00176000
*               GPR15F) UNRESTRICTED;                              0137 00177000
*           END;                    /* LOAD DE(BLDLENTR)           0138 00178000
*                                      ERRET(LOADERR) THE ERRET LABEL   00179000
*                                      SHOULD NEVER RECEIVE CONTROL     00180000
*                                      FROM THIS LOAD. THE ERRET   0138 00181000
*                                      EXISTS TO PREVENT JSINT FROM     00182000
*                                      ABENDING.             @G29ANSS*/ 00183000
*           JSSNTPTR=R0;            /* ADDR OF 1ST SUBSYSTEM NAME IN    00184000
*                                      IEFJSSNT              @G29ANSS*/ 00185000
         LR    JSSNTPTR,R0                                         0139 00186000
*           RFY                                                    0140 00187000
*            (R0,                                                  0140 00188000
*             R15) UNRSTD;          /*                       @G29ANSS*/ 00189000
*                                                                  0140 00190000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00191000
*           /*                                                       */ 00192000
*           /* INITIALIZE THE SUBSYSTEMS - LOOP THROUGH THE          */ 00193000
*           /* SUBSYSTEMS NAMES TABLE. FOR EACH VALID SUBSYSTEM NAME */ 00194000
*           /* ENTRY THAT IS NOT A DUPLICATE, CALL BLDSSCVT TO BUILD */ 00195000
*           /* AN SSCVT AND CHAIN IT TO THE PREVIOUS SSCVT'S @G29ANSS*/ 00196000
*           /*                                                       */ 00197000
*           /*********************************************************/ 00198000
*                                                                  0141 00199000
*           DO WHILE(JSSNTNAM¬=JSSNTEND);/* LOOP UNTIL END OF      0141 00200000
*                                      IEFJSSNT FOUND        @G29ANSS*/ 00201000
         B     @DE00141                                            0141 00202000
@DL00141 DS    0H                                                  0142 00203000
*             IF JSSNTNAM(ONE:ONE)¬=BLANK THEN/* IS ENTRY A DUMMY  0142 00204000
*                                      ENTRY?                @G29ANSS*/ 00205000
         CLI   JSSNTNAM(JSSNTPTR),C' '                             0142 00206000
         BE    @RF00142                                            0142 00207000
*               DO;                 /* NO, VALID SUBSYSTEM NAME    0143 00208000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00209000
*                 CALL SCANSSCT(JSSNTNAM);/* SCAN SSCVT CHAIN      0144 00210000
*                                      SEARCHING FOR A DUPLICATE   0144 00211000
*                                      SUBSYSTEM NAME. DUPSW IS SET     00212000
*                                      ON OR OFF IN SCANSSCT.      0144 00213000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00214000
         ST    JSSNTPTR,@AL00001                                   0144 00215000
         LA    @01,@AL00001                                        0144 00216000
         BAL   @14,SCANSSCT                                        0144 00217000
*                 IF DUPSW=OFF THEN /* ANY DUPLICATES FOUND? @G29ANSS*/ 00218000
         TM    DUPSW,B'10000000'                                   0145 00219000
         BNZ   @RF00145                                            0145 00220000
*                   CALL BLDSSCVT(JSSNTNAM);/* NO, BUILD THE SSCVT 0146 00221000
*                                      FOR THE SUBSYSTEM. PASS THE 0146 00222000
*                                      SUBSYSTEM NAME.       @G29ANSS*/ 00223000
         ST    JSSNTPTR,@AL00001                                   0146 00224000
         LA    @01,@AL00001                                        0146 00225000
         BAL   @14,BLDSSCVT                                        0146 00226000
*               END;                /*                       @G29ANSS*/ 00227000
@RF00145 DS    0H                                                  0148 00228000
*             JSSNTPTR=JSSNTPTR+LENGTH(JSSNTENT);/* GET NEXT ENTRY IN   00229000
*                                      IEFJSSNT              @G29ANSS*/ 00230000
@RF00142 AL    JSSNTPTR,@CF00092                                   0148 00231000
*           END;                    /* OF DO WHILE           @G29ANSS*/ 00232000
@DE00141 CLC   JSSNTNAM(4,JSSNTPTR),@CB00100                       0149 00233000
         BNE   @DL00141                                            0149 00234000
*           DO;                     /* DELETE DE(BLDLENTR)           */ 00235000
*             RESPECIFY                                            0151 00236000
*              (GPR00P) RESTRICTED;                                0151 00237000
*             GPR00P=ADDR(BLDLENTR);/* ->ENTRY NAME                  */ 00238000
         LA    GPR00P,BLDLENTR                                     0152 00239000
*             SVC(9);               /* DELETE SVC                    */ 00240000
         SVC   9                                                   0153 00241000
*             RESPECIFY                                            0154 00242000
*              (GPR00P) UNRESTRICTED;                              0154 00243000
*           END;                    /* DELETE DE(BLDLENTR) DELETE  0155 00244000
*                                      IEFJSSNT              @G29ANSS*/ 00245000
*LOADERR:                                                          0156 00246000
*           ;                       /* THIS LABEL RECEIVES CONTROL 0156 00247000
*                                      FROM THE LOAD FOR IEFJSSNT IF    00248000
*                                      AN ERROR OCCURS. IT SHOULD  0156 00249000
*                                      NEVER RECEIVE CONTROL FROM  0156 00250000
*                                      THERE.                @G29ANSS*/ 00251000

*         END;                      /* OF IEFJSSNT FOUND     @G29ANSS*/ 00253000

*/*  THE FOLLOWING SECTION OF CODE WILL DO:                  @G29AN2F*/ 00257000

*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00387000
*/* PROCEDURE - SCANSSCT                                     @G29ANSS*/ 00388000
*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00389000
*/* FUNCTION  - SCAN THE SSCVT CHAIN SEARCHING FOR A         @G29ANSS*/ 00390000
*/*             SUBSYSTEM NAME WHICH MATCHES THE NAME PASSED @G29ANSS*/ 00391000
*/*             TO THIS ROUTINE.                             @G29ANSS*/ 00392000
*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00393000
*/* OPERATION - SCAN SSCVT CHAIN SEARCHING FOR A MATCH. IF   @G29ANSS*/ 00394000
*/*             FOUND THEN SET DUPSW ON AND RETURN.          @G29ANSS*/ 00395000
*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00396000
*/* INPUT     - JESSSCT: ADDRESS OF THE 1ST SSCVT            @G29ANSS*/ 00397000
*/*             NAMESS : NAME OF SUBSYSTEM SEARCHING FOR     @G29ANSS*/ 00398000
*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00399000
*/* OUTPUT    - DUPSW  : ON IF A MATCH IS FOUND,             @G29ANSS*/ 00400000
*/*                      OFF OTHERWISE                       @G29ANSS*/ 00401000
*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00402000
*/********************************************************************/ 00403000
*                                                                  0191 00404000
*SCANSSCT:                                                         0191 00405000
*   PROC(NAMESS) OPTIONS(NOSAVE,NOSAVEAREA);/*               @G29ANSS*/ 00406000
         B     @EL00001                                            0191 00407000
SCANSSCT MVC   @PC00002(4),0(@01)                                  0191 00408000
*   DCL                                                            0192 00409000
*     NAMESS CHAR(4);               /* NAME OF SUBSYSTEM FOR WHICH A    00410000
*                                      DUPLICATE IS TO BE FOUND.   0192 00411000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00412000
*   DUPSW=OFF;                      /* NO DUPLICATES FOUND YET     0193 00413000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00414000
         NI    DUPSW,B'01111111'                                   0193 00415000
*   SSCTPTR=JESSSCT;                /* BEGINNING OF SSCT CHAIN     0194 00416000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00417000
         L     @10,CVTPTR                                          0194 00418000
         L     @10,CVTJESCT(,@10)                                  0194 00419000
         L     SSCTPTR,JESSSCT(,@10)                               0194 00420000
*   DO WHILE(DUPSW=OFF&SSCTPTR¬=ZERO);/* LOOP UNTIL A DUPLICATE IS 0195 00421000
*                                      FOUND OR THE END OF THE     0195 00422000
*                                      SSCVT'S IS REACHED.   @G29ANSS*/ 00423000
         B     @DE00195                                            0195 00424000
@DL00195 DS    0H                                                  0196 00425000
*     IF NAMESS=SSCTSNAM THEN       /* DUPLICATE SUBSYSTEM NAME?   0196 00426000
*                                                            @G29ANSS*/ 00427000

*       DUPSW=ON;                   /* YES, STOP LOOPING     @G29ANSS*/ 00431000
         OI    DUPSW,B'10000000'                                   0197 00432000
*     ELSE                          /* NO, DUPLICATE NAME    @G29ANSS*/ 00433000
*       SSCTPTR=SSCTSCTA;           /* POINT TO NEXT SSCVT   @G29ANSS*/ 00434000
         B     @RC00196                                            0198 00435000
@RF00196 L     SSCTPTR,SSCTSCTA(,SSCTPTR)                          0198 00436000
*   END;                            /* OF DO WHILE           @G29ANSS*/ 00437000
@RC00196 DS    0H                                                  0199 00438000
@DE00195 TM    DUPSW,B'10000000'                                   0199 00439000
         BNZ   @DC00195                                            0199 00440000
         LTR   SSCTPTR,SSCTPTR                                     0199 00441000
         BNZ   @DL00195                                            0199 00442000
@DC00195 DS    0H                                                  0200 00443000
*   END SCANSSCT;                   /*                       @G29ANSS*/ 00444000
@EL00002 DS    0H                                                  0200 00445000
@EF00002 DS    0H                                                  0200 00446000
@ER00002 BR    @14                                                 0200 00447000
         EJECT                                                          00448000
*                                                                  0201 00449000
*/********************************************************************/ 00450000
*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00451000
*/* PROCEDURE - BLDSSCVT                                     @G29ANSS*/ 00452000
*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00453000
*/* FUNCTION  - BUILD AN SSCVT FOR THE SUBSYSTEM NAME PASSED @G29ANSS*/ 00454000
*/*             AS A PARAMETER.                              @G29ANSS*/ 00455000
*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00456000
*/* OPERATION - . GETMAIN STORAGE FOR THE SSCVT FROM         @G29ANSS*/ 00457000
*/*               SUBPOOL 241.                               @G29ANSS*/ 00458000
*/*             . CHAIN TO THE PREVIOUS SSCVT OR JESCT       @G29ANSS*/ 00459000
*/*             . IF THE SUBSYSTEM IS THE MASTER'S THEN CALL @G29ANSS*/ 00460000

*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00462000

*                                                                  0201 00472000

*   DCL                                                            0202 00482000
*     NAMESUBS CHAR(4);             /* NAME OF SUBSYSTEM FOR WHICH AN   00483000
*                                      SSCVT IS TO BE BUILT. @G29ANSS*/ 00484000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0203 00485000
*    (R0,                                                          0203 00486000
*     R1) RESTRICTED;                                              0203 00487000

         LA    R0,24                                               0204 00489000
*   R0=R0|'F1000000'X;              /* SET SUBPOOL NUMBER            */ 00490000
         O     R0,@CF01108                                         0205 00491000
*   GEN(GETMAIN R,LV=(R0));         /* GET SSCVT CORE                */ 00492000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(R0)                                              00493000
*   SSCTPTR=R1;                     /* SET POINTER TO SSCVT          */ 00494000

*/*                                                                  */ 00543000
*/* PROCEDURE - BLDMSSVT                                     @G29ANSS*/ 00544000
*/*                                                                  */ 00545000
*/* FUNCTION  - CREATE AND INITIALIZE THE MASTER SUBSYSTEM   @G29ANSS*/ 00546000

*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00548000
*/* OPERATION - . GETMAIN THE MASTER SUBSYSTEM VECTOR TABLE  @G29ANSS*/ 00549000

*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00558000

*/*                                                          @G29ANSS*/ 00560000

*                                                                  0220 00562000
*BLDMSSVT:                                                         0220 00563000
*   PROC OPTIONS(SAVE,SAVEAREA);    /*                       @G29ANSS*/ 00564000
*                                                                  0220 00565000

         ST    @13,@SA00004+4                                      0220 00567000
         LA    @14,@SA00004                                        0220 00568000
         ST    @14,8(,@13)                                         0220 00569000
         LR    @13,@14                                             0220 00570000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00571000
*   /*                                                               */ 00572000
*   /* CALCULATE MASTER SUBSYSTEM VECTOR TABLE SIZE: SSVT FIXED AREA */ 00573000
*   /* SIZE PLUS NUMBER OF 'FUNCTION ROUTINE POINTER' FIELDS * 4.    */ 00574000
*   /*                                                               */ 00575000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00576000
*                                                                  0221 00577000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0221 00578000
*    (R6,                                                          0221 00579000
*     R0,                                                          0221 00580000
*     R1) RESTRICTED;                                              0221 00581000
*   R0=LENGTH(SSVTFSIZ)+MSSFUNC*4;                                 0222 00582000
         LA    R0,284                                              0222 00583000
*   R6=R0;                          /* SAVE SSVT LENGTH              */ 00584000
         LR    R6,R0                                               0223 00585000
*   R0=R0|'F1000000'X;              /* SET SUBPOOL NUMBER            */ 00586000
         O     R0,@CF01108                                         0224 00587000
*   GEN(GETMAIN R,LV=(R0));         /* GET MASTER SSVT               */ 00588000
         GETMAIN R,LV=(R0)                                              00589000
*   SSCTSSVT=R1;                    /* SET SSVT POINTER IN SSCVT     */ 00590000
         ST    R1,SSCTSSVT(,SSCTPTR)                               0226 00591000
*/********************************************************************/ 00592000
*/*            FOLLOWING ROUTINE CLEARS GOTTEN CORE:                 */ 00593000
*/*              INPUT:  R1 - BEGINNING ADDRESS OF AREA              */ 00594000
*/*                           TO BE CLEARED                          */ 00595000
*/*                      R6 - LENGTH OF AREA TO BE CLEARED           */ 00596000
*/********************************************************************/ 00597000
*                                                                  0227 00598000
*   DO WHILE(R6>256);                                              0227 00599000
*                                                                  0227 00600000
         B     @DE00227                                            0227 00601000
@DL00227 DS    0H                                                  0228 00602000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00603000
*     /*                                                             */ 00604000
*     /* CLEAR 256 BYTES                                             */ 00605000
*     /*                                                             */ 00606000
*     /***************************************************************/ 00607000
*                                                                  0228 00608000
*     CORAREA(1:256)=CORAREA(1:256)&&CORAREA(1:256);               0228 00609000
         XC    CORAREA(256,R1),CORAREA(R1)                         0228 00610000
*     R6=R6-256;                    /* DECREASE LENGTH OF AREA TO BE    00611000
*                                      CLEARED                       */ 00612000
         LA    @10,256                                             0229 00613000
         SLR   R6,@10                                              0229 00614000
*     R1=R1+256;                    /* BUMP PTR TO AREA TO BE CLEARED*/ 00615000
         ALR   R1,@10                                              0230 00616000
*   END;                                                           0231 00617000
*                                                                  0231 00618000
@DE00227 C     R6,@CF00082                                         0231 00619000
         BH    @DL00227                                            0231 00620000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00621000
*   /*                                                               */ 00622000
*   /* CLEAR REMAINING CORE                                          */ 00623000
*   /*                                                               */ 00624000
*   /*****************************************************************/ 00625000
*                                                                  0232 00626000
*   CORAREA(1:R6)=CORAREA(1:R6)&&CORAREA(1:R6);                    0232 00627000
         LR    @10,R6                                              0232 00628000
         BCTR  @10,0                                               0232 00629000
         EX    @10,@SX01143                                        0232 00630000
*   RESPECIFY                                                      0233 00631000
